research/history/round_summaries/round_0151.json:25:    "self_review": "这轮满足单变量原则：相对 r146 只改 `TRUNK_RANK`。之所以不继续开新 family，是因为 r147 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual`、r148 `two_stage_residual_expert`、r149 `factorized_expert_topk`、r150 `shared_routed_factorized_expert_residual` 已连续给出负信号，当前更值得回答的是“最强兼容 family 还能否向左压成本”。之所以不选更保守的 `TRUNK_RANK=32`，是因为，基于当前成本口径复核，该配置仍位于预期成本带内并满足预算约束。主要风险是旧轮次里 rank<24 往往伴随质量回退，但 r146 的 expert 容量更强，值得做一次明确验证。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0151.json:63:    "self_review": "这轮满足单变量原则：相对 r146 只改 `TRUNK_RANK`。之所以不继续开新 family，是因为 r147 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual`、r148 `two_stage_residual_expert`、r149 `factorized_expert_topk`、r150 `shared_routed_factorized_expert_residual` 已连续给出负信号，当前更值得回答的是“最强兼容 family 还能否向左压成本”。之所以不选更保守的 `TRUNK_RANK=32`，是因为，基于当前成本口径复核，该配置仍位于预期成本带内并满足预算约束。主要风险是旧轮次里 rank<24 往往伴随质量回退，但 r146 的 expert 容量更强，值得做一次明确验证。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0075.json:19:    "hypothesis": "最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = Σ_e Σ_{i∈S_e(x)} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i}，其中 e(x) 是轻量 router 选出的单个 expert，{B_e} 是静态 expert 子库。导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的在线链路仍是“router 选单个静态子库 + 子库内 local top-k + 查表加权求和”，静态库不随样本动态生成，因此 `expert_topk` 属于直接兼容。兼容性先筛清楚：`expert_topk` 直接兼容；`lowrank_expert_topk`、`lowrank_expert_residual`、`two_stage_residual_expert`、`factorized_expert_topk` 属扩展兼容；`batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk` 等 batch/sample-coupled family 属不兼容，不能驱动 frontier。相对 r74 仅把 `NUM_EXPERTS` 从 128 提到 256，在保持 `ARCHITECTURE=expert_topk`、`K=160`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`OPTIMIZER=adam`、`LR=8e-4` 和其余训练配方不变时，继续回答 routed-only MoE-like 前沿的核心问题：如果 r73→r74 的连续改善说明当前低成本带的主要瓶颈仍有一部分来自总静态子库容量不足，而不是 router 质量或 K 预算已经饱和，那么进一步扩大总容量、同时保持 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1` 的短激活路径，应能在仍处于 <0.5x 的近同一 total_cost 下继续压低 FVU，并更清楚地界定这条直接兼容前沿的容量收益何时开始饱和。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0075.json:38:      "如果这一步仍改善，则直接兼容 routed-only 前沿将得到更完整的容量曲线；如果改善停止，可更有把握地把后续结构预算转向 `lowrank_expert_residual` 或 `factorized_expert_topk` 等方向。"
research/history/round_summaries/round_0075.json:42:      "如果 `NUM_EXPERTS=256` 改善极小或停止，则可较清晰判定当前 `expert_topk` 的低成本瓶颈已不主要在总子库容量，后续应把结构预算转回 `lowrank_expert_residual`、`lowrank_expert_topk` 或 `factorized_expert_topk` 这类带 shared basis / trunk / residual cleanup 的兼容结构。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0137.json:25:    "self_review": "这轮满足单轮单变量约束：相对 r136 只改 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT`。它不是继续扫 `K`，也不是回到 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 或 `lowrank_expert_*` 的旧主线，而是对 r136 这个 routed-only 结构做一次关键的 budget reallocation 修正：让 expert 真正变小，看看当前负信号究竟来自结构本身，还是来自过宽 expert 导致的成本/吞吐失衡。主要风险是缩小 per-expert width 后容量不足，FVU 仍可能明显差于当前 low-cost frontier；但如果连这种更符合策略约束的轻量版本也不成立，就可以更干净地把 routed-only 大容量线降级。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0137.json:63:    "self_review": "这轮满足单轮单变量约束：相对 r136 只改 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT`。它不是继续扫 `K`，也不是回到 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 或 `lowrank_expert_*` 的旧主线，而是对 r136 这个 routed-only 结构做一次关键的 budget reallocation 修正：让 expert 真正变小，看看当前负信号究竟来自结构本身，还是来自过宽 expert 导致的成本/吞吐失衡。主要风险是缩小 per-expert width 后容量不足，FVU 仍可能明显差于当前 low-cost frontier；但如果连这种更符合策略约束的轻量版本也不成立，就可以更干净地把 routed-only 大容量线降级。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0211.json:7:  "family_name": "factorized_expert_topk",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0211.json:19:    "hypothesis": "\u5019\u9009 family \u8bbe\u4e3a `factorized_expert_topk`\u3002\u6700\u7ec8\u91cd\u6784\u516c\u5f0f\u5199\u4e3a `x_hat = \u03a3_{e\u2208E(h(x))} \u03a3_{i\u2208S_e(h(x))} \u03b1_{e,i}(h(x)) b_{e,i}`\uff0c\u5176\u4e2d `h(x)=ReLU(Bx)` \u662f\u5171\u4eab\u4f4e\u7ef4 bottleneck\uff0c`E(h(x))` \u662f\u8f7b\u91cf router \u9009\u51fa\u7684\u5c11\u91cf active experts\uff0c`{b_{e,i}}` \u662f\u5404 expert \u7684\u9759\u6001\u5b50\u5e93\u539f\u5b50\uff1b\u5728\u7ebf\u4fa7\u53ef\u76f4\u63a5\u5bfc\u51fa\u4e3a\u201cshared low-rank projection + \u8f7b\u91cf expert \u8def\u7531 + expert \u5b50\u5e93\u67e5\u8868 + \u52a0\u6743\u6c42\u548c + \u9009\u62e9\u6027\u8865\u507f\u201d\u7684 LUTurbo/Lottable \u63a8\u7406\u94fe\u8def\uff0c\u6700\u7ec8\u4ecd\u662f\u9759\u6001\u5411\u91cf\u5e93\u4e0a\u7684\u6709\u9650\u52a0\u6743\u548c\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64\u517c\u5bb9\u6027\u5224\u65ad\u4e3a `\u6269\u5c55\u517c\u5bb9`\u3002`expert_topk`\u3001`shared_routed_expert_topk` \u5c5e\u4e8e\u76f4\u63a5\u517c\u5bb9\uff1b`batch_topk`\u3001`adaptive_budget_topk` \u8fd9\u7c7b batch/sample-coupled family \u4ecd\u5c5e `\u4e0d\u517c\u5bb9`\uff0c\u4e0d\u80fd\u9a71\u52a8\u5f53\u524d objective leaderboard\u3002\u672c\u8f6e\u552f\u4e00\u4e3b\u5047\u8bbe\u662f\uff1ar209\u2192r210 \u5df2\u8bc1\u660e\u201c\u66f4\u5927\u603b\u9759\u6001 expert bank + \u66f4\u5c0f K\u201d\u80fd\u628a routed-only direct-compatible \u4e3b\u7ebf\u538b\u5230 `objective\u22480.365`\uff0c\u4f46\u5f53\u524d\u7f3a\u53e3\u4ecd\u4e3b\u8981\u5728 exceed \u800c\u4e0d\u662f\u7eaf deploy cost\uff1b\u56e0\u6b64\u4e0b\u4e00\u6b65\u6700\u6709\u4fe1\u606f\u91cf\u7684\u95ee\u9898\u4e0d\u662f\u7ee7\u7eed\u5728 `expert_topk` \u4e0a\u505a\u7b2c\u4e09\u8f6e\u5c40\u90e8 K \u63d2\u503c\uff0c\u800c\u662f\u6d4b\u8bd5\u66f4\u8f7b scorer / router \u662f\u5426\u80fd\u5728\u4fdd\u6301 `K=48`\u3001`NUM_EXPERTS=128`\u3001`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`\u3001`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=192` \u7684\u77ed active path \u7ed3\u6784\u4e0b\uff0c\u628a encoder \u9009\u62e9\u6210\u672c\u660e\u663e\u538b\u4f4e\u800c\u4e0d\u628a exceed \u62c9\u574f\u3002\u76f8\u5bf9 r210 \u53ea\u628a `ARCHITECTURE` \u4ece `expert_topk` \u5207\u5230 `factorized_expert_topk`\uff0c\u4fdd\u6301 `EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`\u3001`K=48`\u3001`NUM_EXPERTS=128`\u3001`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`\u3001`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=192`\u3001`FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256`\u3001`adam`\u3001`LR=8e-4` \u4e0e\u5176\u4f59\u8bad\u7ec3\u914d\u65b9\u4e0d\u53d8\uff0c\u76f4\u63a5\u56de\u7b54\u201cexpert \u5185\u90e8 low-rank / shared bottleneck + expert-specific small head\u201d\u8fd9\u6761\u7ed3\u6784\u69fd\u4f4d\uff0c\u662f\u5426\u80fd\u5728\u5f53\u524d small-K \u6210\u672c\u5e26\u5185\u6362\u56de\u66f4\u4f4e objective\u3002\u672c\u5730\u6210\u672c\u590d\u6838\u663e\u793a\u8be5\u70b9\u7684 selection_accesses=393216\u3001deployment_accesses=245760\u3001combined_accesses=638976\uff0c\u5bf9\u5f53\u524d 1024x4096 fused-QKV proxy \u7684 exact total_cost_ratio=0.15234375\uff1b\u76f8\u5bf9 r210 \u7684 exact 0.18359375 \u91ca\u653e\u51fa 0.03125 \u7684 objective \u7a7a\u95f4\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64\u53ea\u8981 exceed \u4fdd\u6301\u5728\u7ea6 0.21298 \u4ee5\u4e0b\uff0c\u5c31\u80fd\u5237\u65b0\u5f53\u524d incumbent\u3002",
