research/history/round_summaries/round_0059.json:20:    "summary": "继续做结构性 low-cost probe，而不是回到 old-family 邻域微调。以 r57 为 matched reference，只增大 `lowrank_expert_topk` 的 routed capacity：`NUM_EXPERTS=16 -> 32`。这保持 trunk/router/active-path 语义不变，却能直接回答 shared+expert 方向在 <0.5x 带内是否仍有容量收益。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0059.json:23:    "family_name": "lowrank_expert_topk",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0059.json:35:      "`lowrank_expert_topk` 已覆盖 `shared trunk + routed expert` 方向，且显式 `NUM_EXPERTS` 走的是真 sparse-capacity mode，不需要新增 family 或新参数接线。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0059.json:36:      "按当前代码的 1024x4096 成本估算，`lowrank_expert_topk K=128 TRUNK_RANK=16 NUM_EXPERTS=32` 约为 仍位于当前目标成本带内，仍稳在 <0.5x 低成本带内。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0059.json:41:      "如果 NUM_EXPERTS=32 基本无改善，则可较清晰判定 r57 的瓶颈不在 routed capacity，而在缺少 residual cleanup；后续应回到 `lowrank_expert_residual` 或 `two_stage_residual_expert`，而不是继续细扫 `lowrank_expert_topk` 的 K/LR。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0059.json:53:    "architecture": "lowrank_expert_topk",
