research/history/round_summaries/round_0082.json:7:  "family_name": "lowrank_expert_topk",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0082.json:19:    "hypothesis": "最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = Σ_{r=1..R} β_r(x) u_r + Σ_{i∈S_{e(x-t(x))}(x-t(x))} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i}，其中 t(x)=Σ_{r=1..R} β_r(x) u_r，U={u_r} 是静态 low-rank trunk 向量库，{B_e} 是静态 expert 子库，e(·) 是轻量 router 选出的单个 expert。导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的在线链路仍是“trunk 查表 + 单 expert 子库查表 + 有限加权和”，静态库不随样本动态生成，因此 `lowrank_expert_topk` 属于扩展兼容。兼容性先筛清楚：`expert_topk` 直接兼容；`lowrank_expert_topk`、`lowrank_expert_residual`、`two_stage_residual_expert` 属扩展兼容；`batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk` 等 batch/sample-coupled family 不兼容，不能驱动 frontier。当前 <0.5x 区域最强点仍是 r60 的 `lowrank_expert_topk`，而最近几轮已分别否定继续压 `TRUNK_RANK`、提高 `STAGE1_RATIO`、以及 trunk-free staged 路线。相对 r60 只把 `NUM_EXPERTS` 从 32 降到 16，在保持 `ARCHITECTURE=lowrank_expert_topk`、`K=128`、`TRUNK_RANK=64`、`STAGE1_RATIO=0.25`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`OPTIMIZER=adam`、`LR=8e-4` 不变时，直接测试当前低成本瓶颈是否包含“expert 子库过度细分导致 router/局部字典划分收益递减”。如果当前 routed capacity 已经够用，那么更粗的 expert 划分应能在几乎不伤 FVU 的前提下小幅降低 selection cost，并把这条 `lowrank + expert` 前沿再向左推一小段。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0082.json:20:    "summary": "Round 82 不继续扫已经给出负信号的 `TRUNK_RANK` / `STAGE1_RATIO`，也不回到 plain selector 的 K/LR 局部微调，而是回到当前最重要的 <0.5x 扩展兼容前沿 `lowrank_expert_topk`。以 r60 为 reference，只改 `NUM_EXPERTS=16`，验证更粗 expert 划分能否以更低总成本保住大部分质量，从而补当前最弱的低开销 Pareto 段。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0082.json:23:    "family_name": "lowrank_expert_topk",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0082.json:25:    "self_review": "满足单轮单变量约束：相对 r60 只改 `NUM_EXPERTS`。这比继续改 `TRUNK_RANK`、回到 `expert_topk` 的 lookup-budget 外推、或继续扩展已被 matched 否定的 trunk-free staged 路线更符合当前证据，因为 r67 已表明在 `lowrank_expert_topk` 上把 `NUM_EXPERTS` 从 32 提到 64 不带来收益，而 r81 又表明当前三段式主线里继续压 trunk 会明显退化；因此当前最值得回答的是低成本 `lowrank + expert` 前沿是否存在“更粗子库、更短路由、更接近经济最优”的一段。主要风险是 `NUM_EXPERTS=16` 会损失局部专门化而让 FVU 回退，但无论正负，这都能直接回答当前低成本区的 expert 粒度是否已过细。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0082.json:35:      "`lowrank_expert_topk` 的 LUTurbo 形式保持不变：静态 trunk 库加单 expert 静态子库上的有限加权和，兼容性为扩展兼容。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0082.json:36:      "在当前代码成本模型下，`lowrank_expert_topk K=128 TRUNK_RANK=64 NUM_EXPERTS=16` 估计 selection ratio 约 0.29、deployment ratio 约 0.19、combined ratio 约 0.47，明显低于 1.5×h×n 硬约束，且比 r60 的 `NUM_EXPERTS=32` 略更靠左。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0082.json:37:      "r67 说明 `lowrank_expert_topk` 上 `NUM_EXPERTS=64` 不优于 `32`；Round 82 用 `32 -> 16` 的反向 probe 来回答当前低成本前沿是否存在更经济的 expert 粒度，而不是继续重复 trunk/stage 轴。"
research/history/round_summaries/round_0082.json:41:      "如果 `NUM_EXPERTS=16` 明显退化，则可以较清楚地判断当前 target 上 `lowrank_expert_topk` 的有效 expert 粒度已接近 `NUM_EXPERTS=32`，后续低成本预算应更多回到 `lowrank_expert_residual` 或转向新的兼容结构，而不是继续在这条 family 上压粗子库。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0082.json:53:    "architecture": "lowrank_expert_topk",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0082.json:62:    "description": "Round 82 不继续扫已经给出负信号的 `TRUNK_RANK` / `STAGE1_RATIO`，也不回到 plain selector 的 K/LR 局部微调，而是回到当前最重要的 <0.5x 扩展兼容前沿 `lowrank_expert_topk`。以 r60 为 reference，只改 `NUM_EXPERTS=16`，验证更粗 expert 划分能否以更低总成本保住大部分质量，从而补当前最弱的低开销 Pareto 段。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0082.json:63:    "self_review": "满足单轮单变量约束：相对 r60 只改 `NUM_EXPERTS`。这比继续改 `TRUNK_RANK`、回到 `expert_topk` 的 lookup-budget 外推、或继续扩展已被 matched 否定的 trunk-free staged 路线更符合当前证据，因为 r67 已表明在 `lowrank_expert_topk` 上把 `NUM_EXPERTS` 从 32 提到 64 不带来收益，而 r81 又表明当前三段式主线里继续压 trunk 会明显退化；因此当前最值得回答的是低成本 `lowrank + expert` 前沿是否存在“更粗子库、更短路由、更接近经济最优”的一段。主要风险是 `NUM_EXPERTS=16` 会损失局部专门化而让 FVU 回退，但无论正负，这都能直接回答当前低成本区的 expert 粒度是否已过细。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0082.json:87:    "ARCHITECTURE": "lowrank_expert_topk",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0082.json:106:    "ARCHITECTURE": "lowrank_expert_topk",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0082.json:129:    "architecture": "lowrank_expert_topk",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0082.json:141:    "family_name": "lowrank_expert_topk",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0082.json:162:    "ARCHITECTURE": "lowrank_expert_topk",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0078.json:19:    "hypothesis": "最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = Σ_e Σ_{i∈S_e(x)} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i}，其中 e(x) 是轻量 router 选出的单个 expert，{B_e} 是静态 expert 子库。导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的在线链路仍是“router 选单个静态子库 + 子库内 local top-k + 查表加权求和”，静态库不随样本动态生成，因此 `expert_topk` 属于直接兼容。兼容性先筛清楚：`expert_topk` 直接兼容；`factorized_expert_topk`、`lowrank_expert_topk`、`lowrank_expert_residual`、`two_stage_residual_expert` 属扩展兼容；`batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk` 等 batch/sample-coupled family 属不兼容，不能驱动 frontier。r77 已经给出清晰负信号：`factorized_expert_topk` 在与 r74 近同成本的 matched probe 下 FVU=0.2482，说明当前 `expert-internal low-rank / shared-basis` 原型不值得继续作为低成本主线。相对 r74 仅把 `K` 从 160 提到 192，在保持 `ARCHITECTURE=expert_topk`、`NUM_EXPERTS=128`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`OPTIMIZER=adam`、`LR=8e-4` 和其余训练配方不变时，直接回答 routed-only MoE-like 低成本前沿的下一关键问题：如果 r73→r74 的连续改善说明当前低成本带的主瓶颈仍有一部分来自每 token 的局部 lookup budget 不足，而不只是总容量，那么在保持同一容量与短 active path 的前提下，适度增加 `K` 应能在仍低于 0.5x total_cost 的范围内继续压低 FVU，并判断 routed-only 低成本线此刻更缺容量还是更缺 lookup budget。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0078.json:20:    "summary": "Round 78 不继续追 r77 已明显失效的 `factorized_expert_topk`，也不回到旧 family 的局部微调；而是在当前最干净、已验证有效的直接兼容 MoE-like 线上做一次高信息量 matched probe。以 r74 为 reference，只把 `K` 从 160 提到 192，直接区分当前 routed-only `expert_topk` 低成本前沿的主要瓶颈究竟还是总容量，还是已经转到单 token 的 lookup budget。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0078.json:36:      "r77 的 matched `factorized_expert_topk` 探针在近同成本下明显弱于 r74，说明当前 `expert-internal low-rank / shared-basis` 原型不值得继续主线推进。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0078.json:63:    "description": "Round 78 不继续追 r77 已明显失效的 `factorized_expert_topk`，也不回到旧 family 的局部微调；而是在当前最干净、已验证有效的直接兼容 MoE-like 线上做一次高信息量 matched probe。以 r74 为 reference，只把 `K` 从 160 提到 192，直接区分当前 routed-only `expert_topk` 低成本前沿的主要瓶颈究竟还是总容量，还是已经转到单 token 的 lookup budget。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0182.json:19:    "hypothesis": "候选 family 设为 `shared_lowrank_two_stage_residual_expert`。最终重构公式为 `x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_sh(h(x))} α_i^sh(x) u_i + Σ_{e∈E(h(x))} Σ_{j∈S_e(r(x))} α_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j}`：其中 `h(x)` 是共享低秩 coarse bottleneck，`{u_i}` 是 shared/coarse 分支的静态向量库，`r(x)=x-x_coarse` 表示经第一阶段 shared/coarse 重构后的残差，`{b_{e,j}}` 是 routed expert residual 子库的静态原子；在线侧先用极便宜的 shared low-rank/coarse 分支吃掉平滑主干，再让少量 routed experts 只做静态 residual 子库上的有限加权和，因此仍可导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“shared/coarse 查表 + routed residual expert 子库查表 + 有限加权和”推理链路，兼容性判断为 `扩展兼容`。`batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk` 这类 batch/sample-coupled family 仍是 `不兼容`，只能作为历史参考，不能驱动当前 frontier。当前额外提示已把问题收束到“保持 very short active path，同时增大总容量，并让 shared/coarse branch 负责主干、routed experts 只做 sparse residual cleanup”；在已知 `expert_topk` 与 `shared_routed_factorized_expert_topk` 都给出新的低成本负信号后，当前最有信息量的下一问不是继续在同一 family 补 `K/LATENTS`，而是用一个真正改变‘容量与激活路径关系’的结构槽位做 matched architecture probe。相对 r165 只把 `ARCHITECTURE` 从 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 切到 `shared_lowrank_two_stage_residual_expert`，保持 `K=108`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=160`、`NUM_EXPERTS=64`、`FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256`、`STAGE1_RATIO=0.25`、`adam`、`LR=8e-4` 与其余训练配方不变，直接测试“cheap shared/coarse + routed residual cleanup”是否比近期失败的 routed-only / fully-factorized 方向更接近当前 low-cost anchors。，基于当前成本口径复核，该配置仍位于预期成本带内并满足预算约束。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0182.json:25:    "self_review": "这轮严格遵守 param_only 单变量约束：相对 r165 只改 `ARCHITECTURE`。虽然当前阶段强调 `<0.25x` 主战场，但在最近两轮已经连续否定 routed-only 与 fully-factorized low-cost 变体后，用一个仍留在 `0.25x-0.35x` 辅助带内、且真正改变“shared 主干 vs residual cleanup”分工关系的结构槽位做 probe，信息增量高于继续在线性 `K/LATENTS` 轴上补点。选择 `shared_lowrank_two_stage_residual_expert` 而不是 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk`，是因为它更贴合本轮新增提示里“先用极便宜 shared/coarse branch 吃掉平滑主干，再让 routed experts 只做 sparse residual cleanup”的结构假设。主要风险是该 family 属于已被部分下调优先级的 shared-lowrank/two-stage 类别；但它是当前仍处在低成本辅助带、且与最新策略提示最匹配的现成结构。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0182.json:36:      "本轮是 architecture-level probe，不是继续在 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 主线内补 `K/LATENTS_PER_EXPERT` 插值。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0182.json:37:      "最近低成本 probes 已给出负信号：r176 的 routed-only `expert_topk` 在约 `0.20x` 下仍明显偏弱，r177 的 `shared_routed_factorized_expert_topk` 在约 `0.20x` 下更差；当前这一步是更符合新策略提示的“cheap shared/coarse + residual experts”结构测试。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0182.json:43:      "如果该点仍明显弱于当前 `shared_routed_expert_topk` anchors，且也不能优于 r176/r177，则可更明确地下调当前 target 上两段式 shared-lowrank residual-expert 方向优先级，转向别的 very-light residual / factorized 槽位。"
research/history/round_summaries/round_0182.json:64:    "self_review": "这轮严格遵守 param_only 单变量约束：相对 r165 只改 `ARCHITECTURE`。虽然当前阶段强调 `<0.25x` 主战场，但在最近两轮已经连续否定 routed-only 与 fully-factorized low-cost 变体后，用一个仍留在 `0.25x-0.35x` 辅助带内、且真正改变“shared 主干 vs residual cleanup”分工关系的结构槽位做 probe，信息增量高于继续在线性 `K/LATENTS` 轴上补点。选择 `shared_lowrank_two_stage_residual_expert` 而不是 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk`，是因为它更贴合本轮新增提示里“先用极便宜 shared/coarse branch 吃掉平滑主干，再让 routed experts 只做 sparse residual cleanup”的结构假设。主要风险是该 family 属于已被部分下调优先级的 shared-lowrank/two-stage 类别；但它是当前仍处在低成本辅助带、且与最新策略提示最匹配的现成结构。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0182.json:88:    "ARCHITECTURE": "shared_routed_expert_topk",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0215.json:19:    "hypothesis": "\u5019\u9009 family \u8bbe\u4e3a `shared_two_stage_residual_expert`\u3002\u6700\u7ec8\u91cd\u6784\u516c\u5f0f\u5199\u4e3a x_hat = \u03a3_{i\u2208S_sh(x)} \u03b1_i^sh(x) u_i + \u03a3_{e\u2208E(r(x))} \u03a3_{j\u2208S_e(r(x))} \u03b3_{e,j}(r(x)) b_{e,j}\uff0c\u5176\u4e2d r(x)=x-\u03a3_{i\u2208S_sh(x)} \u03b1_i^sh(x) u_i\uff1b{u_i} \u662f\u9759\u6001 shared/coarse \u5411\u91cf\u5e93\uff0c{b_{e,j}} \u662f\u9759\u6001 routed residual expert \u5b50\u5e93\u3002\u5728\u7ebf\u4fa7\u4ecd\u53ef\u76f4\u63a5\u5bfc\u51fa\u5230 LUTurbo/Lottable \u7684\u201cshared/coarse \u67e5\u8868 + residual expert \u5b50\u5e93\u67e5\u8868 + \u6709\u9650\u52a0\u6743\u548c + \u5fc5\u8981\u65f6\u9009\u62e9\u6027\u5728\u7ebf\u8865\u507f\u201d\u94fe\u8def\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64 `shared_two_stage_residual_expert` \u5c5e\u4e8e `\u6269\u5c55\u517c\u5bb9`\u3002`expert_topk`\u3001`shared_routed_expert_topk` \u5c5e\u4e8e `\u76f4\u63a5\u517c\u5bb9`\uff1b`batch_topk`\u3001`adaptive_budget_topk` \u7b49 batch/sample-coupled family \u5c5e\u4e8e `\u4e0d\u517c\u5bb9`\uff0c\u4e0d\u80fd\u9a71\u52a8\u5f53\u524d objective leaderboard\u3002\u5f53\u524d incumbent r212 \u5df2\u628a routed-only `expert_topk` \u538b\u5230 exact total_cost_ratio=0.1640625\uff0c\u4f46 r213 \u4e0e r214 \u8fde\u7eed\u7ed9\u51fa\u4e92\u8865\u8d1f\u4fe1\u53f7\uff1a\u7ee7\u7eed\u628a routed-only sparse path \u538b\u5230 `K=16` \u4f1a\u8ba9 exceed \u5931\u63a7\uff0c\u800c\u53ea\u52a0\u4fbf\u5b9c low-rank trunk \u4e5f\u4e0d\u8db3\u4ee5\u628a exceed \u538b\u56de\u53ef\u8d62\u533a\u95f4\u3002\u8fd9\u8bf4\u660e\u5f53\u524d\u672a\u51b3\u7684\u9ad8\u4ef7\u503c\u95ee\u9898\u5df2\u4ece\u201c\u8fd8\u80fd\u5426\u7ee7\u7eed\u538b cost\u201d\u8f6c\u5411\u201c\u663e\u5f0f shared/coarse \u4e3b\u5e72 + residual cleanup \u662f\u5426\u80fd\u5728\u53ef\u63a5\u53d7 cost \u5185\u66f4\u6709\u6548\u5730\u63a7\u5236 tail error\u201d\u3002\u56e0\u6b64\u76f8\u5bf9 r212 \u4ec5\u628a `ARCHITECTURE` \u4ece `expert_topk` \u5207\u5230 `shared_two_stage_residual_expert`\uff0c\u4fdd\u6301 `K=32`\u3001`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`\u3001`NUM_EXPERTS=128`\u3001`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`\u3001`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=192`\u3001`STAGE1_RATIO=0.25`\u3001`FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256`\u3001`TRUNK_RANK=16`\u3001`adam`\u3001`LR=8e-4` \u4e0e\u5176\u4f59\u8bad\u7ec3\u914d\u65b9\u4e0d\u53d8\uff0c\u76f4\u63a5\u6d4b\u8bd5\u201c\u4e0d\u5bf9\u79f0 coarse+cleanup \u5206\u5de5\u201d\u662f\u5426\u80fd\u5728\u5f53\u524d hookpoint \u4e0b\u5f62\u6210\u6bd4 routed-only \u548c cheap-trunk-only \u66f4\u597d\u7684 objective \u4ea4\u6362\u7387\u3002\u672c\u5730\u6210\u672c\u590d\u6838\u663e\u793a\u8be5\u70b9 selection_accesses=720896\u3001deployment_accesses=163840\u3001combined_accesses=884736\uff0c\u5bf9\u5f53\u524d 1024x4096 fused-QKV proxy \u7684 exact total_cost_ratio=0.2109375\uff1b\u76f8\u5bf9 r212 \u7684 exact 0.1640625 \u589e\u52a0\u4e86 0.046875 \u7684\u6210\u672c\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64\u82e5\u8981\u5237\u65b0 incumbent\uff0c\u9700\u8981 exceed \u538b\u5230\u7ea6 0.1486625 \u4ee5\u4e0b\u3002\u8fd9\u4e2a\u95e8\u69db\u5f88\u6fc0\u8fdb\uff0c\u4f46\u5b83\u6b63\u662f\u5f53\u524d\u6700\u503c\u5f97\u56de\u7b54\u7684\u7ed3\u6784\u95ee\u9898\uff1ashared/coarse \u5206\u652f\u82e5\u4e0d\u80fd\u663e\u8457\u7f13\u89e3 online compensation \u9700\u6c42\uff0c\u5c31\u4e0d\u5e94\u7ee7\u7eed\u5360\u7528\u540e\u7eed\u9884\u7b97\u3002",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0215.json:25:    "self_review": "\u8fd9\u8f6e\u4e25\u683c\u6ee1\u8db3\u5355\u53d8\u91cf\u539f\u5219\uff1a\u76f8\u5bf9 r212 \u53ea\u6539 `ARCHITECTURE`\u3002\u5728\u8fde\u7eed\u4e24\u8f6e no-improve \u540e\uff0c\u7ee7\u7eed\u56f4\u7ed5 `expert_topk` \u505a `K`\u3001`ACTIVE_EXPERTS` \u6216\u5176\u5b83\u5c40\u90e8\u63d2\u503c\u7684\u4fe1\u606f\u589e\u91cf\u5df2\u7ecf\u660e\u663e\u4e0b\u964d\uff0c\u4e0d\u7b26\u5408\u5f53\u524d\u7b56\u7565\u9ed8\u8ba4\u8981\u6c42\u3002\u9009\u62e9 `shared_two_stage_residual_expert` \u800c\u4e0d\u662f `shared_routed_expert_topk` \u6216\u518d\u6b21\u56de\u5230 factorized/lowrank \u5bb6\u65cf\uff0c\u662f\u56e0\u4e3a\u5b83\u66f4\u76f4\u63a5\u5bf9\u5e94\u5f53\u524d\u6700\u9ad8\u4f18\u5148\u7ea7\u7684\u201c\u4e0d\u5bf9\u79f0 shared/coarse \u5403\u4e3b\u5e72\u3001routed experts \u505a residual cleanup\u201d\u65b9\u5411\uff0c\u800c\u4e14 current-target \u5386\u53f2\u4e0a\u5b83\u4e5f\u662f\u5269\u4f59\u517c\u5bb9\u7ed3\u6784\u91cc\u6700\u63a5\u8fd1 incumbent \u7684\u65b0 family\u3002\u4e3b\u8981\u98ce\u9669\u662f\u8be5 family \u5373\u4f7f\u5728\u66f4\u9ad8 K \u4e0b\u5386\u53f2\u6700\u597d exceed \u4e5f\u4ecd\u5728 0.17-0.19 \u4e00\u5e26\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64\u8981\u5728 `K=32`\u3001cost\u22480.21x \u4e0b\u76f4\u63a5\u6253\u5230 0.1487 \u4ee5\u4e0b\u5e76\u4e0d\u5bb9\u6613\uff1b\u4f46\u5982\u679c\u8fde\u8fd9\u6761\u6700\u8d34\u5408\u5f53\u524d\u7b56\u7565\u5047\u8bbe\u7684 family \u90fd\u505a\u4e0d\u5230\uff0c\u540e\u7eed\u5c31\u53ef\u4ee5\u66f4\u679c\u65ad\u5730\u4e0b\u8c03\u6574\u4e2a coarse+cleanup \u7ebf\u5728\u5f53\u524d hookpoint \u7684\u4f18\u5148\u7ea7\u3002",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0215.json:37:      "r214 \u5df2\u660e\u786e\u7ed9\u51fa cheap-trunk-only \u8d1f\u4fe1\u53f7\uff1a`lowrank_expert_topk K=32 TRUNK_RANK=16 NUM_EXPERTS=128 ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2 LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=192` \u7684 exact total_cost_ratio=0.19140625\u3001exceed=0.187566\u3001objective=0.378973\uff0c\u8bf4\u660e\u4ec5\u9760\u4fbf\u5b9c trunk \u8fd8\u4e0d\u8db3\u4ee5\u628a exceed \u62c9\u56de\u53ef\u8d62\u533a\u95f4\u3002",
