research/history/round_summaries/round_0222.json:19:    "hypothesis": "\u5019\u9009 family \u8bbe\u4e3a `lowrank_residual`\u3002\u6700\u7ec8\u91cd\u6784\u516c\u5f0f\u5199\u4e3a `x_hat = \u03a3_r \u03b2_r(x) u_r + \u03a3_{i\u2208S(x-trunk(x))} \u03b1_i(x) b_i`\uff0c\u5373 `x_hat = trunk(x) + sparse_residual(x)`\uff1b\u5176\u4e2d `{u_r}` \u662f\u9759\u6001 low-rank trunk \u5411\u91cf\u5e93\uff0c`{b_i}` \u662f\u9759\u6001 residual \u5411\u91cf\u5e93\u3002\u5728\u7ebf\u4fa7\u53ef\u76f4\u63a5\u5bfc\u51fa\u5230 LUTurbo/Lottable \u7684\u201clow-rank trunk \u67e5\u8868/\u52a0\u6743\u548c + residual \u5e93\u9009\u62e9 + residual \u5e93\u67e5\u8868 + \u6709\u9650\u52a0\u6743\u6c42\u548c + \u9009\u62e9\u6027\u8865\u507f\u201d\u63a8\u7406\u94fe\u8def\uff0c\u9759\u6001\u5e93\u4e0d\u968f\u6837\u672c\u52a8\u6001\u751f\u6210\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64\u8be5 family \u5224\u5b9a\u4e3a `\u6269\u5c55\u517c\u5bb9`\u3002`expert_topk`\u3001`lowrank_expert_topk`\u3001`shared_routed_expert_topk` \u7b49\u4ecd\u662f\u517c\u5bb9 family\uff1b`batch_topk`\u3001`adaptive_budget_topk` \u7b49 batch/sample-coupled family \u4ecd\u5c5e `\u4e0d\u517c\u5bb9`\uff0c\u4e0d\u80fd\u9a71\u52a8\u5f53\u524d objective leaderboard\u3002\u672c\u8f6e\u552f\u4e00\u4e3b\u5047\u8bbe\u662f\uff1a\u5728 factorized selector\u3001factorized residual\u3001shared-lowrank\u3001shared+routed \u7b49\u66f4\u590d\u6742\u65b9\u5411\u8fde\u7eed\u5931\u5229\u4e4b\u540e\uff0c\u5f53\u524d remaining compatible families \u91cc\u6700\u503c\u5f97\u505a matched probe \u7684\u4e0d\u662f\u518d\u53e0\u52a0\u95e8\u63a7/\u5206\u7ec4\u7ec6\u8282\uff0c\u800c\u662f\u5148\u56de\u5230\u6700\u7b80\u5355\u3001\u6700\u53ef\u89e3\u91ca\u7684 `plain low-rank trunk + sparse residual` \u57fa\u51c6\u7ed3\u6784\uff0c\u76f4\u63a5\u56de\u7b54 trunk+residual \u8fd9\u6761\u4e3b\u7ebf\u5728\u5f53\u524d target \u4e0a\u662f\u5426\u8fd8\u6709\u7ee7\u7eed\u4ef7\u503c\u3002\u76f8\u5bf9 r212 \u4ec5\u628a `ARCHITECTURE` \u4ece `expert_topk` \u5207\u5230 `lowrank_residual`\uff0c\u4fdd\u6301 `K=32`\u3001`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`\u3001`OPTIMIZER=adam`\u3001`LR=8e-4` \u4ee5\u53ca\u5176\u4f59\u4e3b recipe \u4e0d\u53d8\uff0c\u76f4\u63a5\u6d4b\u8bd5\u201cplain trunk + sparse residual \u662f\u5426\u80fd\u5728\u65e0\u989d\u5916 expert/router \u590d\u6742\u5ea6\u7684\u60c5\u51b5\u4e0b\u663e\u8457\u538b\u4f4e exceed\u201d\u3002\u672c\u5730\u590d\u6838\u663e\u793a\u8be5\u70b9 selection_accesses=1081344\u3001deployment_accesses=245760\u3001combined_accesses=1327104\uff0c\u5bf9\u5f53\u524d 1024x4096 fused-QKV proxy \u7684 exact total_cost_ratio=0.31640625\uff1b\u76f8\u5bf9 r212 \u7684 exact 0.1640625 \u589e\u52a0\u4e86 0.15234375\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64\u82e5\u8981\u5237\u65b0\u5f53\u524d anchor\uff0c\u9700\u8981 exceed \u538b\u5230\u7ea6 `\u22640.0391312575`\u3002\u8fd9\u4e2a\u95e8\u69db\u663e\u7136\u6781\u5176\u6fc0\u8fdb\uff0c\u6240\u4ee5\u672c\u8f6e\u4e0d\u662f\u9ad8\u80dc\u7387\u7ffb\u76d8\u70b9\uff0c\u800c\u662f\u4e00\u8f6e\u5fc5\u8981\u7684\u7ed3\u6784\u88c1\u51b3\uff1a\u5982\u679c\u8fde\u6700\u5e72\u51c0\u7684 lowrank trunk + sparse residual \u90fd\u7ed9\u4e0d\u51fa\u63a5\u8fd1\u53ef\u884c\u7684 exceed \u4ea4\u6362\u7387\uff0c\u90a3\u4e48\u6574\u4e2a plain residual \u4e3b\u7ebf\u5728\u5f53\u524d hookpoint \u4e0a\u5c31\u53ef\u4ee5\u7cfb\u7edf\u6027\u964d\u7ea7\u3002",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0062.json:20:    "summary": "r61 已证明三段式 `lowrank_expert_residual` 在当前更强的 trunk+expert 配方上优于纯 `lowrank_expert_topk`。Round 62 不再加成本，而是做同成本预算重分配：只降 `STAGE1_RATIO`，直接回答当前收益更依赖 expert 段还是 residual cleanup 段。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0062.json:41:      "如果它明显变差，则说明当前更强 trunk+expert 配方下，expert 段仍不能再缩，后续应优先考虑压 `K` 或回到 `lowrank_expert_topk` 的更低成本延展，而不是继续给 residual 段加预算。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0062.json:62:    "description": "r61 已证明三段式 `lowrank_expert_residual` 在当前更强的 trunk+expert 配方上优于纯 `lowrank_expert_topk`。Round 62 不再加成本，而是做同成本预算重分配：只降 `STAGE1_RATIO`，直接回答当前收益更依赖 expert 段还是 residual cleanup 段。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0156.json:19:    "hypothesis": "最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_sh(h(x))} α_i^sh(h(x)) u_i + Σ_{e∈E(h(x))} Σ_{j∈S_e(x-t(x))} γ_{e,j}(x) c_{e,j}，其中 h(x)=ReLU(Bx)，t(x)=Σ_{i∈S_sh(h(x))} α_i^sh(h(x)) u_i，U={u_i} 是静态 shared 向量库，{C_e} 是静态 expert residual 子库。导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 时仍是“shared low-rank projection + shared library lookup + residual 上的 expert-local top-k + 有限加权和”，静态库不随样本动态生成，因此该 family 判定为扩展兼容；`batch_topk` / `adaptive_budget_topk` 等不兼容 family 仍不能驱动 frontier。本轮唯一主假设是：r155 已经把 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk @ K=96` 明确证伪为当前 0.28x 低成本带的有效前沿候选，因此下一步不应继续在同一 family 上做局部扫参，而应切到另一条仍符合当前 agenda 的新结构槽位。相对当前低成本参考 r152，只把 `ARCHITECTURE` 从 `lowrank_expert_residual` 切到 `shared_lowrank_two_stage_residual_expert`，保持 `K=96`、`EF=1`、`FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256`、`NUM_EXPERTS=64`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=224`、`STAGE1_RATIO=0.25` 与其余训练 recipe 不变，直接回答“shared low-rank coarse stage + expert residual cleanup”在约 0.28x total_cost 下是否比已失败的 shared-lowrank routed top-k 更接近当前低成本 frontier。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0156.json:35:      "r155 已落盘：`shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk @ K=96` 实际 FVU=0.14630839228630066，显著落后当前 0.28x-0.30x 低成本 frontier，因此不应继续在该 family 上做局部扫参。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0156.json:39:      "这轮是对另一条高优先级结构槽位 `two-stage residual expert` 的 matched-cost 重验，不是继续打磨 `lowrank_expert_*` 或已失败的 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk`。"
research/history/round_summaries/round_0107.json:7:  "family_name": "shared_routed_expert_topk",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0107.json:19:    "hypothesis": "最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_shared(x)} α_i^sh(x) b_i^sh + Σ_{e∈E(x)} Σ_{j∈S_e(x)} α_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j}，其中 B^sh 是始终激活的静态 shared 子库，E(x) 是轻量 router 选出的少量 routed experts，所有原子都来自静态向量库，因此在线侧仍可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“shared 子库查表 + routed 子库查表 + 有限加权和”链路，兼容性判断为直接兼容。明确排除不兼容 family：`batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk` 等 batch/sample-coupled 结构不能驱动 frontier。本轮唯一主假设是：r106 已证明 shared+routed 在 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=512, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2` 下有真实质量信号，FVU 已压到 0.0981，但该点约 0.52x total_cost，仍略高于当前最需要补强的 <0.5x 带，且尚未形成新的非支配点。相对 r106 仅把 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT` 从 512 降到 384，在保持 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`、`NUM_EXPERTS=64`、`K=128`、`EF=1` 与其余训练配方不变时，正好对应 operator guide 指向的 matched-cost“更窄 per-expert width + 多 routed experts”左移测试；按当前 cost proxy 估算，总成本将约从 0.52x 降到 0.42x，若 FVU 仍能明显优于当前 <0.5x 主线 `lowrank_expert_topk K=128` 的 0.1193，则 shared+routed 将在低成本带形成新的结构性 Pareto 段。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0107.json:23:    "family_name": "shared_routed_expert_topk",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0107.json:35:      "r106 已给出 shared+routed 的强正信号：`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=512, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2` 下 val_fvu=0.09808561205863953，明显优于当前 <0.5x 主线 `lowrank_expert_topk K=128` 的 0.119261234998703。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0107.json:36:      "按当前 1024x4096 cost proxy 估算，`shared_routed_expert_topk K=128 EF=1 NUM_EXPERTS=64 ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2 LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=384` 的 selection≈0.30x、deployment≈0.12x、total≈0.42x，仍远低于 1.5×h×n 硬预算。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0107.json:41:      "如果 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=384` 明显退化到接近或差于 `lowrank_expert_topk`，则可初步判定当前 shared+routed 收益仍依赖较宽 expert；后续应减少这条 family 的预算，把低成本探索切回 `lowrank_expert_topk` 的 `TRUNK_RANK` / `K` knee。",
