research/history/logs/agent_action_0070.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"TRUNK_RANK","value":"32"}],"expected_win":"lower_cost","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_expert_topk","family_stage":"prototype","hypothesis":"Final reconstruction stays x_hat = sum_{r=1..R} beta_r(x) u_r + sum_{i in S_{e(x-t(x))}(x-t(x))} alpha_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i}, with t(x) = sum_{r=1..R} beta_r(x) u_r. This exports to the LUTurbo/Lottable path as a static trunk table lookup plus a single routed static expert sublibrary lookup plus a finite weighted sum, so `lowrank_expert_topk` is extended-compatible. Compatibility screen before proposing this round: `expert_topk` is directly compatible; `lowrank_expert_topk`, `lowrank_expert_residual`, and `two_stage_residual_expert` are extended-compatible; batch-coupled families such as `batch_topk` and `adaptive_budget_topk` are incompatible and must stay off the active frontier. Relative to r60, changing only `TRUNK_RANK` from 64 to 32 tests the missing mid-trunk point in the low-cost band: if the routed-only improvement from r59 to r60 was not all-or-nothing, this should recover much of r60's FVU while moving left from the current lowrank+expert anchor and potentially create a new compatible Pareto segment between `expert_topk` and `lowrank_expert_residual`.","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["If `TRUNK_RANK=32` keeps most of r60 quality at materially lower total_cost, next do a matched `ARCHITECTURE=lowrank_expert_residual` switch from this point to measure whether residual cleanup is still worth paying for at the same trunk width.","If `TRUNK_RANK=32` falls back close to the routed-only `expert_topk` band, treat that as evidence that `lowrank_expert_topk` has a sharp trunk-width floor and shift low-cost budget back to `lowrank_expert_residual` or pure `expert_topk` rather than more MoE-capacity expansion.","If throughput or convergence looks anomalous rather than simply worse, use a follow-up midpoint such as `TRUNK_RANK=48` before drawing a structural conclusion."],"notes_to_memory":["Round 70 targets the under-mapped low-to-mid-cost region with a structural width probe, not another plain-K sweep.","`lowrank_expert_topk` now has informative anchors at `TRUNK_RANK=16` and `64` under `K=128, NUM_EXPERTS=32`; `TRUNK_RANK=32` is the clean missing midpoint for the same compatible family.","Keep incompatible batch-coupled families excluded from frontier accounting; active frontier decisions should continue to use only direct-compatible and extended-compatible families."],"reference_round":60,"self_review":"This satisfies the single-variable param-only rule and stays within an already implemented compatible family. It directly answers a higher-value structural question than another `expert_topk` K move, and it avoids spending Round 70 on further local polishing of the current `lowrank_expert_residual` mainline after r66 already showed diminishing returns from more trunk compression there.","summary":"Use Round 70 for a low-cost structural probe in `lowrank_expert_topk`: start from r60 and only reduce `TRUNK_RANK` to 32. The goal is to map whether shared low-rank trunk width can produce a new compatible Pareto point in the 0.3x-0.5x band, instead of continuing plain-selector K sweeps or more local cleanup on `lowrank_expert_residual`.","touched_files":[]}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0206.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_sh(x)} α_i^sh(x) u_i + Σ_{e∈E(r(x))} Σ_{j∈S_e(r(x))} γ_{e,j}(r(x)) b_{e,j}，其中 r(x)=x-Σ_{i∈S_sh(x)} α_i^sh(x) u_i；{u_i} 是静态 shared/coarse 向量库，{b_{e,j}} 是静态 routed residual expert 子库。在线侧仍可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“shared/coarse 查表 + routed residual expert 子库查表 + 有限加权和 + 必要时选择性在线补偿”链路，因此 `shared_two_stage_residual_expert` 属扩展兼容；`expert_topk`、`shared_routed_expert_topk` 属直接兼容；`batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk` 等 batch/sample-coupled family 属不兼容，不能驱动当前 objective leaderboard。r205 已经在 exact same cost=0.210938x 下证明把 `STAGE1_RATIO` 从 0.25 压到 0.125 会让 objective 从 0.398672 恶化到 0.403221、exceed 从 0.187735 回弹到 0.192283，说明当前这条 two-stage 线并不是 coarse 过重、cleanup 预算不足，而更像 coarse 主干仍偏弱。本轮唯一主假设是：相对 r201 仅把 `STAGE1_RATIO` 从 0.25 提到 0.375，保持 `ARCHITECTURE=shared_two_stage_residual_expert`、`K=64`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=160`、`NUM_EXPERTS=64`、`TRUNK_RANK=16`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`adam`、`LR=8e-4` 与其余配方不变，测试在 exact total_cost 不变的前提下，给 shared/coarse 主干更多 K 预算是否能比 r201 更有效地降低 exceed_alpha_0.50，并把 objective 进一步推近 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 的 0.3952 乃至 incumbent r199 的 0.3861。","summary":"建议以 r201 为 reference，只改 `STAGE1_RATIO=0.375`。这轮继续留在 `shared_two_stage_residual_expert`，不是低信息细扫，而是对 r205 的反向 exact-cost 验证：既然更多 cleanup 预算在同成本下已被证伪，当前最有价值的未决问题就是更强 coarse 主干是否才是这条 family 真正缺的那一块。","change_type":"param_only","expected_win":"lower_objective","family_name":"shared_two_stage_residual_expert","family_stage":"prototype","self_review":"这轮严格满足单变量原则：相对 r201 只改 `STAGE1_RATIO`。之所以允许继续留在同一 family，而不是立刻切到全新结构槽位，是因为这里仍有一个高价值且尚未验证完的结构假设：`shared_two_stage_residual_expert` 是当前 target 上最接近 incumbent 的新 family，且 `STAGE1_RATIO` 是极少数可以在 exact cost 不变条件下直接回答“主干 vs cleanup 谁才是瓶颈”的旋钮。r205 已经明确否定了“更多 residual cleanup 预算会更好”这一方向，因此本轮反向测 `0.375` 不是线性插值，而是对该 family 核心分工假设的闭环验证。主要风险是更重 coarse 会让 residual cleanup 不足，导致 exceed 不降反升；但如果如此，就能更明确地结束这条 family 在 `K=64` lane 的预算分工问题，不再继续消耗轮次。","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"STAGE1_RATIO","value":"0.375"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["r205 已给出明确负信号：`shared_two_stage_residual_expert K=64 A=2 L=160 STAGE1_RATIO=0.125` 在 exact same cost=0.210938x 下把 objective 从 r201 的 0.398672 恶化到 0.403221，exceed 从 0.187735 回弹到 0.192283，说明把更多 K 预算让给 residual cleanup 并不成立。","当前 `shared_two_stage_residual_expert` 仍是最接近 incumbent 的新结构 family：r201 objective=0.398672 cost=0.210938x exceed=0.187735；它比 r200 `lowrank_expert_topk` 的 0.402860 和 r205 的 0.403221 都更好。","本地 exact cost 复核已通过：`shared_two_stage_residual_expert K=64 A=2 L=160` 在 `STAGE1_RATIO=0.125/0.25/0.375/0.5` 下 combined_accesses 都固定为 884736，对当前 1024x4096 proxy 的 actual total_cost_ratio 固定为 0.210938x。","override allowlist 本地校验已通过：`validate_env_overrides([{key: STAGE1_RATIO, value: 0.375}], fallback_architecture='shared_two_stage_residual_expert')` 返回空列表。"],"next_hypotheses":["如果 `STAGE1_RATIO=0.375` 在 exact same cost 下显著优于 r201，并把 objective 压到接近或优于 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 的 0.3952，则下一轮保持该 family 不变，只改 `K=80`，测试更强 coarse 主干配更高 deploy budget 是否能进一步换回更低 exceed。","如果 `STAGE1_RATIO=0.375` 与 r201 基本持平或更差，则说明 `shared_two_stage_residual_expert` 在当前 `K=64` lane 的主干/cleanup 分工问题已经基本摸清；后续应停止在该 family 上继续细扫，转回新的 architecture slot。","如果 `STAGE1_RATIO=0.375` 只带来小幅改善但仍明显落后于 incumbent，则记录为 two-stage 线需要更强 coarse 而非更多 cleanup，但它在当前主战场仍不足以形成 regime shift；后续除非出现新的高价值结构假设，否则不应继续主导预算。"],"reference_round":201}
