research/history/round_summaries/round_0226.json:73:    "self_review": "\u8fd9\u8f6e\u4e25\u683c\u6ee1\u8db3\u5355\u53d8\u91cf\u539f\u5219\uff1a\u76f8\u5bf9 r212 \u53ea\u6539 `ARCHITECTURE`\uff0c\u6ca1\u6709\u65b0\u589e\u53c2\u6570\uff0c\u4e5f\u6ca1\u6709\u4ee3\u7801\u6539\u52a8\u3002\u6ca1\u6709\u518d\u9009 `lowrank_expert_residual`\u3001`two_stage_residual_expert`\u3001`whitened_lowrank_residual`\u3001`codebook_topk` \u7b49\u672a\u6d4b family\uff0c\u662f\u56e0\u4e3a\u672c\u5730 exact cost \u590d\u6838\u663e\u793a\u5b83\u4eec\u5728\u5f53\u524d matched recipe \u4e0b\u90fd\u843d\u5728 `0.38x+`\uff0c\u5df2\u7ecf\u5728 objective \u4e0a\u5148\u9a8c\u65e0\u6cd5\u5237\u65b0 incumbent\uff1b\u7ee7\u7eed\u6d4b\u8bd5\u5b83\u4eec\u66f4\u50cf\u8d28\u91cf\u951a\u70b9\uff0c\u4e0d\u7b26\u5408\u672c\u8f6e\u201cmatched architecture probe\u201d\u4f18\u5148\u56de\u7b54 objective \u69fd\u4f4d\u4ef7\u503c\u7684\u8981\u6c42\u3002\u76f8\u6bd4 `topk` \u4e0e `group_topk`\uff0c`jumprelu` \u5728\u540c exact cost \u4e0b\u63d0\u4f9b\u4e86\u6700\u660e\u786e\u7684\u652f\u6301\u5f62\u6210\u673a\u5236\u53d8\u5316\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64\u4fe1\u606f\u589e\u91cf\u66f4\u9ad8\u3002\u4e3b\u8981\u98ce\u9669\u540c\u6837\u660e\u786e\uff1a\u5b83\u8981\u8d62\u8fc7 r212 \u9700\u8981\u628a exceed \u76f4\u63a5\u6253\u5230\u7ea6 `0.0665`\uff0c\u73b0\u5b9e\u95e8\u69db\u5f88\u9ad8\uff0c\u6240\u4ee5\u8fd9\u66f4\u50cf\u6700\u540e\u4e00\u4e2a direct-compatible selector closure probe\uff0c\u800c\u4e0d\u662f\u9ad8\u7f6e\u4fe1\u7ffb\u76d8\u70b9\u3002",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0273.json:26:    "self_review": "\u8fd9\u8f6e\u6ee1\u8db3\u5355\u53d8\u91cf\u539f\u5219\uff1a\u8fd0\u884c\u914d\u7f6e\u76f8\u5bf9 r266 \u53ea\u6539 `ARCHITECTURE`\u3002\u4ee3\u7801\u4fa7\u65b0\u589e family \u5df2\u5b8c\u6210\u6700\u5c0f\u5fc5\u8981\u63a5\u7ebf\uff0c\u5e76\u8865\u4e86 compatibility registry \u8bb0\u5f55\uff1b\u6ca1\u6709\u5f15\u5165\u65b0 tunable key\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64\u4e0d\u9700\u8981\u6539 `config_resolution`\u3001`runner` \u6216 `scripts/autoresearch_test.sh`\u3002\u4e3b\u8981\u98ce\u9669\u662f dense trunk \u5e26\u6765\u7684\u989d\u5916 deploy cost\uff08\u76f8\u5bf9 r266 \u591a `0.013671875x`\uff09\u6362\u4e0d\u56de\u8db3\u591f\u7684 exceed \u6539\u5584\uff1b\u4f46\u8fd9\u6b63\u662f\u4e00\u4e2a\u9ad8\u4fe1\u606f\u91cf\u7684 matched architecture probe\uff0c\u80fd\u76f4\u63a5\u56de\u7b54\u201cshared sparse coarse\u201d\u662f\u5426\u771f\u7684\u662f\u5f53\u524d scaffold \u5fc5\u9700\u4ef6\u3002",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0273.json:45:      "\u517c\u5bb9\u6027\u6ce8\u518c\u8868\u5df2\u8865\u5145\u8be5 family\uff0c\u5f53\u524d\u89e3\u6790\u7ed3\u679c\u4e3a `extended_compatible`\u3002"
research/history/round_summaries/round_0273.json:78:    "self_review": "\u8fd9\u8f6e\u6ee1\u8db3\u5355\u53d8\u91cf\u539f\u5219\uff1a\u8fd0\u884c\u914d\u7f6e\u76f8\u5bf9 r266 \u53ea\u6539 `ARCHITECTURE`\u3002\u4ee3\u7801\u4fa7\u65b0\u589e family \u5df2\u5b8c\u6210\u6700\u5c0f\u5fc5\u8981\u63a5\u7ebf\uff0c\u5e76\u8865\u4e86 compatibility registry \u8bb0\u5f55\uff1b\u6ca1\u6709\u5f15\u5165\u65b0 tunable key\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64\u4e0d\u9700\u8981\u6539 `config_resolution`\u3001`runner` \u6216 `scripts/autoresearch_test.sh`\u3002\u4e3b\u8981\u98ce\u9669\u662f dense trunk \u5e26\u6765\u7684\u989d\u5916 deploy cost\uff08\u76f8\u5bf9 r266 \u591a `0.013671875x`\uff09\u6362\u4e0d\u56de\u8db3\u591f\u7684 exceed \u6539\u5584\uff1b\u4f46\u8fd9\u6b63\u662f\u4e00\u4e2a\u9ad8\u4fe1\u606f\u91cf\u7684 matched architecture probe\uff0c\u80fd\u76f4\u63a5\u56de\u7b54\u201cshared sparse coarse\u201d\u662f\u5426\u771f\u7684\u662f\u5f53\u524d scaffold \u5fc5\u9700\u4ef6\u3002",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0183.json:20:    "hypothesis": "最终重构公式设为 `x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_sh(x)} α_i^sh(x) u_i + Σ_{e∈E(r(x))} Σ_{j∈S_e(r(x))} γ_{e,j}(r(x)) b_{e,j}`，其中 `r(x)=x-Σ_{i∈S_sh(x)} α_i^sh(x) u_i`。`{u_i}` 是静态 shared coarse library，`{b_{e,j}}` 是静态 routed expert residual 子库；在线链路仍是“shared 查表+加权和 -> residual router 选少量 expert 子库 -> 子库查表+加权和”，不引入动态字典，因此该 family 判定为 `扩展兼容`。`batch_topk`/`adaptive_budget_topk` 这类 batch/sample-coupled family 仍属 `不兼容`，不能驱动当前 frontier。唯一主假设是：当前 low-cost gap 可能不在 shared 分支是否存在，而在 shared 与 routed 分支没有明确分工；把 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 改成显式的“shared coarse trunk + routed residual cleanup”，并保持与 r165 同一 `K=108, EF=1, NUM_EXPERTS=64, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=160, STAGE1_RATIO=0.25` 的 matched-cost recipe，可在 `<0.25x` 主战场直接测试这种分工是否优于当前 joint-topk baseline。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0183.json:93:    "ARCHITECTURE": "shared_routed_expert_topk",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0049.json:7:  "family_name": "lowrank_expert_topk",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0049.json:17:    "hypothesis": "最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = Σ_{r=1..R} β_r(x) u_r + Σ_{i∈S_{e(x-t(x))}(x-t(x))} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i}，其中 t(x)=Σ_{r=1..R} β_r(x) u_r。也就是先用静态 low-rank trunk 向量库 U={u_r} 重构平滑主干，再对残差用轻量 router 选择单个静态 expert 子库 B_e={b_{e,i}} 并做局部 sparse 选择；因此它仍可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“trunk 查表 + expert 子库查表 + 有限加权和”推理链路，兼容性判定为扩展兼容。r48 已明确表明当前 blocker 仍然是运行时构造路径：policy behavioral diff 通过 `from sparsify import SparseCoder` 直接实例化时，`cfg.architecture=lowrank_expert_topk` 仍未生效，导致比较结果依旧变成 topk vs topk。本轮主任务是继续修复 `sparsify/sparse_coder.py` 中的直接构造分发，让 `SparseCoder(1024, SparseCoderConfig(architecture='lowrank_expert_topk', ...))` 真正返回对应 family，然后按 r42 仅改 `TRUNK_RANK=128` 的原计划重跑，拿到这条 `lowrank + expert` 结构在约 0.44x total_cost 下的首个有效点。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0049.json:18:    "summary": "Round 48 证明 blocker 还没有消除：`lowrank_expert_topk` 再次在 behavioral diff 阶段被误拦，而且这次 round summary 显示并没有真正落地代码补丁。当前优先级最高的是继续做最小 repair，而不是回到 `lowrank_expert_residual` 再打磨一个低成本邻域点；先把 `SparseCoder(..., cfg)` 的分发修通，再重跑相对 r42 仅改 `TRUNK_RANK=128` 的低成本 probe，才能把 `lowrank_expert_topk` 的成败当成结构证据。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0049.json:21:    "family_name": "lowrank_expert_topk",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0049.json:23:    "self_review": "满足当前阶段的运行时优先级：先消除重复 blocker，再做架构比较。代码改动范围仍只限 `sparsify/`，不改 evaluation semantics，也不改 AutoResearch/launcher；实验配置相对 r42 仍只改一个 env 参数 `TRUNK_RANK=128`。这次 repair 需要按架构集成 checklist 做完整验证：修复直接构造分发、用完全相同的 `architecture=lowrank_expert_topk, K=192, EF=1` 做 instantiate/forward/backward smoke，并确认 behavioral diff 不再把它判成 topk。风险是修复后该 family 的真实效果可能仍不强；但那时才是有效结构结论。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0049.json:35:      "r48 之后可以确认：当前 blocker 仍是 `SparseCoder(..., cfg)` 直接构造路径没有正确尊重 `cfg.architecture`，而不是 `lowrank_expert_topk` 本身的结构质量。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0049.json:36:      "`lowrank_expert_topk` 的 LUTurbo 形式仍是静态 trunk 库 + 单 expert 静态子库上的有限加权和，属于扩展兼容 family。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0049.json:37:      "按当前成本估算，`lowrank_expert_topk K=192 EF=1 TRUNK_RANK=128` 的 total_cost 约为 0.44x；修复 blocker 后应优先获得这个点的真实 FVU。"
research/history/round_summaries/round_0049.json:41:      "如果 repair 后该点仍明显弱于 `jumprelu` 或 `lowrank_expert_residual` 的低成本点，则应归档 `lowrank_expert_topk`，把预算转回其他高优先级结构方向。",
