research/history/round_summaries/round_0239.json:78:    "self_review": "\u8fd9\u8f6e\u6ca1\u6709\u7ee7\u7eed\u56f4\u7ed5 `expert_jumprelu` \u505a\u4f4e\u4fe1\u606f\u7ec6\u626b\uff0c\u800c\u662f\u6309\u5f53\u524d\u72b6\u6001 `consecutive_no_improve=2` \u5207\u5230\u65b0\u7684\u7ed3\u6784\u69fd\u4f4d\uff0c\u7b26\u5408\u4e3b\u7ebf\u7b56\u7565\u3002\u9009\u62e9 `lowrank_expert_jumprelu` \u800c\u4e0d\u662f `lowrank_expert_residual`\uff0c\u56e0\u4e3a\u672c\u5730\u7cbe\u786e\u6210\u672c\u590d\u6838\u663e\u793a\u524d\u8005 combined_accesses=802816\u3001total_cost_ratio=0.19140625\uff0c\u4ecd\u5728\u5f53\u524d\u4f18\u5148\u7684 0.14x-0.20x \u5e26\uff1b\u540e\u8005\u4f1a\u76f4\u63a5\u5230 0.44x\uff0c\u4fe1\u606f\u5bc6\u5ea6\u592a\u4f4e\u3002\u8be5 family \u4e0e\u73b0\u6709\u5b9e\u73b0\u7684\u7cbe\u786e\u5dee\u5f02\u4e0d\u662f\u91cd\u547d\u540d\uff1a\u5b83\u628a `lowrank_expert_topk` \u7684 expert-local top-k \u652f\u6491\u6362\u6210 `expert_jumprelu` \u5f0f\u5e73\u6ed1\u95e8\u63a7\uff0c\u4ece\u800c\u6d4b\u8bd5 trunk \u662f\u5426\u80fd\u8ba9 small-K \u8def\u7ebf\u7684 exceed \u9000\u5316\u66f4\u6162\u3002\u4e3b\u8981\u98ce\u9669\u4e5f\u5f88\u660e\u786e\uff1a\u8981\u5728 0.1914x \u6210\u672c\u4e0b\u51fb\u8d25\u5f53\u524d incumbent 0.35449\uff0c\u9700\u8981 exceed \u538b\u5230\u7ea6 0.1631 \u4ee5\u4e0b\uff0c\u8fd9\u4e2a\u95e8\u69db\u4e0d\u4f4e\uff1b\u5982\u679c\u8fd9\u8f6e\u4ecd\u505a\u4e0d\u5230\uff0c\u5c31\u5e94\u5feb\u901f\u4e0b\u8c03\u8fd9\u6761 lowrank+JumpReLU \u7ed3\u6784\u7ebf\uff0c\u800c\u4e0d\u662f\u7ee7\u7eed\u8865\u5c40\u90e8\u63d2\u503c\u3002",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0050.json:7:  "family_name": "lowrank_expert_topk",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0050.json:17:    "hypothesis": "最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = Σ_{r=1..R} β_r(x) u_r + Σ_{i∈S_{e(x-t(x))}(x-t(x))} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i}，其中 t(x)=Σ_{r=1..R} β_r(x) u_r。也就是先用静态 low-rank trunk 向量库 U={u_r} 重构平滑主干，再对残差用轻量 router 选择单个静态 expert 子库 B_e={b_{e,i}} 并做局部 sparse 选择；因此它仍可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“trunk 查表 + expert 子库查表 + 有限加权和”推理链路，兼容性判定为扩展兼容。Round 48 和 Round 49 都表明 blocker 仍然是运行时构造路径，而不是结构质量：policy behavioral diff 通过 `from sparsify import SparseCoder` 直接实例化时，`cfg.architecture=lowrank_expert_topk` 仍未生效，比较结果依旧变成 topk vs topk。本轮主任务是继续修复 `sparsify/sparse_coder.py` 中的直接构造分发，让 `SparseCoder(1024, SparseCoderConfig(architecture='lowrank_expert_topk', ...))` 真正返回对应 family，然后按 r42 仅改 `TRUNK_RANK=128` 的原计划重跑，拿到这条 `lowrank + expert` 结构在约 0.44x total_cost 下的首个有效点。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0050.json:18:    "summary": "当前最高优先级仍是消除重复 blocker，而不是继续在 `lowrank_expert_residual` 上打磨低成本邻域点。r48、r49 连续两轮都显示 `lowrank_expert_topk` 在 behavioral diff 阶段被误拦，且 round summary 里 `touched_files=[]`、`patch_path=null`，说明修复并未真正落地；因此 Round 50 应继续做最小 repair，把 `SparseCoder(..., cfg)` 的分发修通，再重跑相对 r42 仅改 `TRUNK_RANK=128` 的低成本 probe。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0050.json:21:    "family_name": "lowrank_expert_topk",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0050.json:23:    "self_review": "满足当前阶段的运行时优先级：先消除 blocker，再做结构比较。代码改动范围仍只限 `sparsify/`，不改 evaluation semantics，也不改 AutoResearch/launcher；实验配置相对 r42 仍只改一个 env 参数 `TRUNK_RANK=128`。这次 repair 需要给出可验证的完成标准：1. 直接构造 `SparseCoder(..., cfg)` 时按 `cfg.architecture` 分发；2. 用完全相同的 `architecture=lowrank_expert_topk, K=192, EF=1` 做 instantiate/forward/backward smoke；3. behavioral diff 不再把它判成 topk。风险是修复后该 family 的真实效果可能仍不强；但那时才是有效结构结论，而不是观测链路伪影。",
