research/history/round_summaries/round_0104.json:37:      "fresh cost 估算：`shared_routed_expert_topk K=128 EF=1 NUM_EXPERTS=64` 的 selection≈0.52x、deployment≈0.12x、total≈0.64x，仍在允许的 0.3x-0.8x 结构 anchor 带内。"
