research/history/round_summaries/round_0059.json:20:    "summary": "继续做结构性 low-cost probe，而不是回到 old-family 邻域微调。以 r57 为 matched reference，只增大 `lowrank_expert_topk` 的 routed capacity：`NUM_EXPERTS=16 -> 32`。这保持 trunk/router/active-path 语义不变，却能直接回答 shared+expert 方向在 <0.5x 带内是否仍有容量收益。",
