research/history/round_summaries/round_0241.json:20:    "hypothesis": "\u6700\u7ec8\u91cd\u6784\u516c\u5f0f\u8bbe\u4e3a x_hat = \u03a3_{e\u2208E_pk(x)} \u03a3_{i\u2208S_e^\u03c4(x)} \u03b1_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i}\u3002\u5176\u4e2d\u6bcf\u4e2a expert \u5b50\u5e93 {b_{e,i}} \u90fd\u662f\u9759\u6001\u5411\u91cf\u5e93\uff0cE_pk(x) \u4e0d\u662f\u7531 full router \u6216 fixed hash \u76f4\u63a5\u7ed9\u51fa\uff0c\u800c\u662f\u7531\u4e24\u8def learned product-key \u8def\u7531\u5206\u6570\u76f8\u52a0\u540e\u5728\u7b1b\u5361\u5c14 expert \u5bf9\u4e0a\u9009\u51fa\u5c11\u91cf active experts\uff1alogit_e(x)=l_{a(e)}(x)+r_{b(e)}(x)\uff1bexpert \u5185\u90e8\u518d\u7528 JumpReLU \u5f62\u6210\u5c40\u90e8 support S_e^\u03c4(x)\u3002\u5728\u7ebf\u5bfc\u51fa\u94fe\u8def\u4ecd\u662f\u201cleft/right product-key router \u6253\u5206 -> \u9009\u62e9\u5c11\u91cf\u9759\u6001 expert \u5b50\u5e93 -> expert \u5185 JumpReLU sparse support -> \u67e5\u8868\u52a0\u6743\u6c42\u548c -> \u9009\u62e9\u6027\u8865\u507f\u201d\uff0c\u4e0d\u4f9d\u8d56\u52a8\u6001\u751f\u6210\u5b57\u5178\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64\u517c\u5bb9\u6027\u5224\u65ad\u4e3a\u76f4\u63a5\u517c\u5bb9\u3002`batch_topk`\u3001`adaptive_budget_topk` \u8fd9\u7c7b batch/sample-coupled family \u4ecd\u662f\u4e0d\u517c\u5bb9\uff0c\u4e0d\u80fd\u8fdb\u5165\u5f53\u524d objective leaderboard\u3002\u672c\u8f6e\u552f\u4e00\u4e3b\u5047\u8bbe\u662f\uff1a\u5f53\u524d incumbent `expert_jumprelu@K32` \u7684 objective \u7f3a\u53e3\u4ecd\u4e3b\u8981\u5361\u5728 selection cost\uff0c\u800c recent `hashed_expert_jumprelu` \u4e0e `factorized_router_expert_topk` \u7684\u8d1f\u4fe1\u53f7\u8bf4\u660e\u201c\u628a router \u53d8\u8f7b\u201d\u672c\u8eab\u4e0d\u80fd\u9760 fixed hash \u6216 generic low-rank hidden \u7c97\u66b4\u5b8c\u6210\uff1b\u76f8\u5bf9 r235 \u4ec5\u628a `ARCHITECTURE` \u4ece `expert_jumprelu` \u5207\u5230\u65b0\u5b9e\u73b0\u7684 `product_key_expert_jumprelu`\uff0c\u4fdd\u6301 `K=32`\u3001`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`\u3001`NUM_EXPERTS=128`\u3001`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`\u3001`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=192`\u3001`adam`\u3001`LR=8e-4` \u4e0e\u5176\u4f59 recipe \u4e0d\u53d8\uff0c\u76f4\u63a5\u6d4b\u8bd5 PKM-style coarse-to-fine compositional routing \u662f\u5426\u80fd\u5728\u4fdd\u4f4f routed micro-expert \u8d28\u91cf\u7684\u540c\u65f6\uff0c\u628a exact total_cost_ratio \u538b\u5230 0.138427734375\uff0c\u5e76\u628a exceed_alpha_0.50 \u7ef4\u6301\u5728\u7ea6 0.2161 \u4ee5\u4e0b\uff0c\u4ece\u800c\u5237\u65b0\u5f53\u524d incumbent 0.354491\u3002\u8fd9\u4e2a family \u4e0e\u5df2\u6d4b `factorized_router_expert_topk` \u7684\u7cbe\u786e\u5dee\u5f02\u662f\uff1a\u5b83\u4e0d\u662f\u201c\u4f4e\u79e9 hidden -> \u5168 expert logits\u201d\uff0c\u800c\u662f\u201c\u5de6\u53f3\u4e24\u7ec4\u5c0f key \u7684\u53ef\u7ec4\u5408 expert addressing\u201d\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64\u662f\u5728\u5f53\u524d target \u4e0a\u5c1a\u672a\u88ab\u73b0\u6709 family \u8986\u76d6\u7684\u65b0\u7ed3\u6784\u69fd\u4f4d\u3002",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0257.json:35:      "\u5de5\u4f5c\u533a\u771f\u5b9e\u517c\u5bb9 frontier \u4ecd\u4ee5 `research/history/frontier.json` \u4e3a\u51c6\uff1ar251 `product_key_expert_jumprelu` \u662f\u5f53\u524d best compatible objective \u70b9\uff1bprompt \u91cc\u7684\u65e7 `expert_jumprelu` anchor \u5df2\u8fc7\u65f6\uff0c\u4e0d\u5e94\u7ee7\u7eed\u5f53\u9ed8\u8ba4\u4e3b\u7ebf\u3002",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0257.json:37:      "r252-r256 \u5df2\u8fde\u7eed\u7ed9\u51fa\u8d1f\u4fe1\u53f7\uff1a`NUM_EXPERTS=256`\u3001`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1`\u3001`hashed_expert_jumprelu`\u3001`factorized_router_expert_topk`\u3001`shared_lowrank_two_stage_residual_expert` \u90fd\u6ca1\u6709\u628a objective \u62c9\u56de r251 \u9644\u8fd1\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64\u4e0b\u4e00\u6b65\u6700\u503c\u5f97\u5148\u56de\u7b54\u7684\u662f PK \u4e3b\u7ebf\u662f\u5426\u53d7 `K=32` \u7684 deploy budget \u9650\u5236\u3002",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0079.json:19:    "hypothesis": "最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = Σ_{r=1..R} β_r(x) u_r + Σ_{i∈S_{e(x)}(x)} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i} + Σ_j γ_j(x) c_j，其中 U={u_r} 是静态 low-rank trunk 向量库，{B_e} 是静态 expert 子库，C={c_j} 是静态 residual 补偿库。导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的在线链路仍是“trunk 查表 + 单 expert 子库查表 + residual 补偿查表 + 有限加权和”，静态库不随样本动态生成，因此 `lowrank_expert_residual` 属于扩展兼容。兼容性先筛清楚：`expert_topk` 直接兼容；`lowrank_expert_topk`、`lowrank_expert_residual`、`two_stage_residual_expert`、`factorized_expert_topk` 属扩展兼容；`batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk` 等 batch/sample-coupled family 属不兼容，不能驱动 frontier。r77 与 r78 已给出清晰负信号：shared-basis `factorized_expert_topk` 明显弱于 matched `expert_topk`，而 routed-only `expert_topk` 把 `K` 从 160 提到 192 也进一步退化，说明当前低成本带的主瓶颈已不主要在 routed-only scorer 或 lookup budget。相对 r76 仅把 `STAGE1_RATIO` 从 0.25 提到 0.5，在保持 `ARCHITECTURE=lowrank_expert_residual`、`K=128`、`TRUNK_RANK=32`、`NUM_EXPERTS=64`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`OPTIMIZER=adam`、`LR=8e-4` 和其余训练配方不变时，直接回答当前三段式低成本主线的关键未决问题：r76 的容量扩展未继续改善，究竟是因为 routed expert 总容量已饱和，还是因为当前 `stage1_k` 只占总 K 的 25%，导致新增 expert 容量根本没有被足够激活。如果后者成立，那么在几乎不改变总成本的前提下，把更多在线预算分给 expert stage、减少全局 residual cleanup，应能在当前低到中成本带继续压低 FVU，并更清楚界定这条 `lowrank + expert + residual` 前沿真正需要的 budget split。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0146.json:19:    "hypothesis": "最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_r β_r(x) u_r + Σ_{i∈S_{e(x)}(x)} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i} + Σ_j γ_j(x) c_j，其中 U={u_r} 是静态 low-rank trunk 向量库，{B_e} 是静态 expert 子库，C={c_j} 是静态全局 residual 库。在线侧可导出为“low-rank trunk 查表/加权和 + expert 子库 local top-k + residual library lookup + 有限加权和”，静态库不随样本动态生成，因此 `lowrank_expert_residual` 判定为扩展兼容，不是不兼容 family。唯一主假设：相对 r143 仅把 `ARCHITECTURE` 从 `lowrank_expert_topk` 切到 `lowrank_expert_residual`，保持 `K=112`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`TRUNK_RANK=40`、`NUM_EXPERTS=64`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=224`、`STAGE1_RATIO=0.25` 与其余训练配方不变，直接回答“在当前已有效的 lowrank+expert 低成本配方上再加一段全局 residual cleanup”是否能以约 0.54x total_cost 换来足够大的 FVU 改善，从而形成新的中成本 Pareto 段。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0146.json:20:    "summary": "建议以 r143 为 reference，只改 `ARCHITECTURE=lowrank_expert_residual`。这是一轮结构扩展对照：在当前已有效的 `lowrank_expert_topk` 低成本配方上加一段全局 residual cleanup，直接测试它能否在约 0.54x total_cost 下形成新的中成本 Pareto 段。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0146.json:25:    "self_review": "这轮满足单轮单变量约束：相对 r143 只改 `ARCHITECTURE`。r143 提供了新的低成本可行锚点，而 r145 已清楚回答“单 expert 压缩”不可行；继续沿 `lowrank_expert_topk` 做内部扫参的信息增量开始下降。切到 `lowrank_expert_residual` 更符合当前阶段对 `lowrank + expert + residual` 这一高优先级方向的补证据需求，也避免重新把预算投入旧 family 的局部邻域。主要风险是该点落在 >0.5x 带宽，但策略已允许保留少量质量锚点，这轮的价值在于直接回答 residual cleanup 是否值得这部分额外成本。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0146.json:35:      "r145 已明确给出负信号：`lowrank_expert_topk` 的质量仍依赖 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`，把 expert 激活路径压到单 expert 会从 r143 的 FVU=0.1273 回退到 0.1971。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0146.json:36:      "本轮不是继续在 `lowrank_expert_topk` 上做局部扫参，而是切到高优先级结构槽位 `lowrank + expert + residual`，直接测试 residual cleanup 的结构增益。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0146.json:42:      "如果该点明显劣于预期，则可以更明确地把当前主线保留在 `lowrank_expert_topk` 的低成本段，并下调现有 `lowrank + expert + residual` 配方在当前 target 上的优先级。"
