research/history/round_summaries/round_0044.json:20:    "summary": "Round 43 的 `lowrank_expert_topk` 被 policy 的 behavioral-diff blocker 拦截，这一轮先不把预算继续投到被运行时策略卡住的 family，而是沿当前最强且已验证兼容的 `lowrank_expert_residual` 继续向低成本带延伸。以 r37 为参考仅下调 `TRUNK_RANK` 到 16，预计把总成本从约 1.06x 压到约 0.52x，直接回答这条三段式结构在接近 0.5x 区域是否还能保持明显优于现有低成本 anchor 的质量。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0044.json:25:    "self_review": "满足单轮单变量约束：相对 r37 只改 `TRUNK_RANK`。这不是旧 family 的局部 K 轴打磨，而是在当前主线结构上做一次高信息量的成本压缩试验；相比继续追 `lowrank_expert_topk`，它避免再次撞上已知 policy blocker。风险是 `TRUNK_RANK=16` 比 r38 的 128 更激进，FVU 可能明显恶化；但这正是本轮要回答的核心问题，即 lowrank+expert+residual 在接近 0.5x 带时是否仍然成立。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0044.json:37:      "Round 43 的阻塞来自 policy 侧 behavioral diff 对 `lowrank_expert_topk` 的拦截，不应把那次 `policy_reject` 误判为结构质量结论。"
research/history/round_summaries/round_0044.json:62:    "description": "Round 43 的 `lowrank_expert_topk` 被 policy 的 behavioral-diff blocker 拦截，这一轮先不把预算继续投到被运行时策略卡住的 family，而是沿当前最强且已验证兼容的 `lowrank_expert_residual` 继续向低成本带延伸。以 r37 为参考仅下调 `TRUNK_RANK` 到 16，预计把总成本从约 1.06x 压到约 0.52x，直接回答这条三段式结构在接近 0.5x 区域是否还能保持明显优于现有低成本 anchor 的质量。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0044.json:63:    "self_review": "满足单轮单变量约束：相对 r37 只改 `TRUNK_RANK`。这不是旧 family 的局部 K 轴打磨，而是在当前主线结构上做一次高信息量的成本压缩试验；相比继续追 `lowrank_expert_topk`，它避免再次撞上已知 policy blocker。风险是 `TRUNK_RANK=16` 比 r38 的 128 更激进，FVU 可能明显恶化；但这正是本轮要回答的核心问题，即 lowrank+expert+residual 在接近 0.5x 带时是否仍然成立。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0142.json:19:    "hypothesis": "最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_sh(h(x))} α_i^sh(h(x)) b_i^sh + Σ_{e∈E(h(x))} Σ_{j∈S_e(h(x))} α_{e,j}(h(x)) b_{e,j}，其中 h(x)=ReLU(Bx) 是共享低秩投影，{b_i^sh} 是 shared 静态向量库，{b_{e,j}} 是 routed expert 静态子库。在线侧可导出为“shared low-rank projection + shared library lookup + routed expert local top-k + 有限加权和”，静态库不随样本动态生成，因此 `shared_routed_factorized_expert_topk` 判定为直接兼容，不是不兼容 family。唯一主假设：相对 r123 仅把 `ARCHITECTURE` 从 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 切到 `shared_routed_factorized_expert_topk`，保持 `K=112`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`、`FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=224`、`NUM_EXPERTS=64` 与其余训练配方不变，直接回答“shared+routed 异构 MoE 中把 expert 内部 scorer 也做低秩化”是否能在约 0.22x total_cost 下形成新的低成本结构段。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0142.json:25:    "self_review": "这轮满足单轮单变量约束：相对 r123 只改 `ARCHITECTURE`。在 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual` 连续两轮非支配失败、`shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 也已给出新的负信号后，继续沿同一 family 做局部压缩信息增量偏低；切到 `shared_routed_factorized_expert_topk` 更符合当前对异构 MoE 与 expert-internal low-rank 的优先级，也能在更低的 0.22x 成本带补一段此前仍欠清晰的结构证据。主要风险是该 family 在旧轮次已有弱负信号，但当前这次是与 r123 严格 matched-cost 的 fresh validation，结论更有解释力。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0142.json:35:      "r141 已说明 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 在约 0.30x total_cost 下仍被当前 low-cost frontier 压制，因此“shared low-rank basis + full expert head”这条无 residual 线可暂时降级。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0142.json:42:      "如果结果只小幅优于 `expert_topk` 但仍被 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 支配，则说明 shared branch 有价值，但 routed experts 过度低秩化会伤害质量；后续应优先保留 expert-specific full heads 或切向别的 staged/residual 结构。"
research/history/round_summaries/round_0142.json:63:    "self_review": "这轮满足单轮单变量约束：相对 r123 只改 `ARCHITECTURE`。在 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual` 连续两轮非支配失败、`shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 也已给出新的负信号后，继续沿同一 family 做局部压缩信息增量偏低；切到 `shared_routed_factorized_expert_topk` 更符合当前对异构 MoE 与 expert-internal low-rank 的优先级，也能在更低的 0.22x 成本带补一段此前仍欠清晰的结构证据。主要风险是该 family 在旧轮次已有弱负信号，但当前这次是与 r123 严格 matched-cost 的 fresh validation，结论更有解释力。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0142.json:87:    "ARCHITECTURE": "shared_routed_expert_topk",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0208.json:7:  "family_name": "lowrank_expert_topk",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0208.json:19:    "hypothesis": "\u6700\u7ec8\u91cd\u6784\u516c\u5f0f\u4fdd\u6301\u4e3a x_hat = \u03a3_r \u03b2_r(x) u_r + \u03a3_{j\u2208S_{e(x-t(x))}(x-t(x))} \u03b1_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j}\uff0c\u5176\u4e2d t(x)=\u03a3_r \u03b2_r(x) u_r\uff1b{u_r} \u662f\u9759\u6001 low-rank trunk \u5411\u91cf\u5e93\uff0c{b_{e,j}} \u662f\u9759\u6001 expert \u5b50\u5e93\u3002\u5728\u7ebf\u4fa7\u4ecd\u53ef\u5bfc\u51fa\u5230 LUTurbo/Lottable \u7684\u201ctrunk \u67e5\u8868/\u52a0\u6743\u548c + \u8f7b\u91cf router \u9009\u5c11\u91cf expert \u5b50\u5e93 + expert \u5b50\u5e93\u67e5\u8868/\u52a0\u6743\u548c + \u5fc5\u8981\u65f6\u9009\u62e9\u6027\u5728\u7ebf\u8865\u507f\u201d\u94fe\u8def\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64 `lowrank_expert_topk` \u5224\u5b9a\u4e3a\u6269\u5c55\u517c\u5bb9\uff1b`expert_topk`\u3001`shared_routed_expert_topk` \u5c5e\u76f4\u63a5\u517c\u5bb9\uff1b`batch_topk`\u3001`adaptive_budget_topk` \u7b49 batch/sample-coupled family \u5c5e\u4e0d\u517c\u5bb9\uff0c\u4e0d\u80fd\u9a71\u52a8\u5f53\u524d objective leaderboard\u3002r207 \u5df2\u7ecf\u628a `lowrank_expert_topk K=64 ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2 LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=160 TRUNK_RANK=16` \u63a8\u5230 objective=0.396871\u3001cost=0.199219x\u3001exceed=0.197653\uff0c\u8fd9\u4e2a\u70b9\u4e0e incumbent r199 \u7684\u5dee\u8ddd 0.010757 \u91cc\uff0c\u7edd\u5927\u90e8\u5206\u6765\u81ea cost \u800c\u4e0d\u662f exceed\uff1b\u540c\u65f6 family \u5185\u5df2\u6709\u65c1\u8bc1 r175 vs r170 \u8868\u660e\u5728\u66f4\u9ad8 K\u3001\u66f4\u5bbd latent \u7684 recipe \u4e0a\u628a `TRUNK_RANK` \u4ece 16 \u538b\u5230 8 \u80fd\u4ee5\u66f4\u4f4e cost \u6362\u6765\u66f4\u4f4e objective\uff0c\u800c\u4e0d\u662f\u5fc5\u7136\u9020\u6210 tail error \u7206\u70b8\u3002\u672c\u8f6e\u552f\u4e00\u4e3b\u5047\u8bbe\u662f\uff1a\u76f8\u5bf9 r207 \u4ec5\u628a `TRUNK_RANK` \u4ece 16 \u538b\u5230 8\uff0c\u4fdd\u6301 `ARCHITECTURE=lowrank_expert_topk`\u3001`K=64`\u3001`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`\u3001`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=160`\u3001`NUM_EXPERTS=64`\u3001`FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256`\u3001`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`\u3001`adam`\u3001`LR=8e-4` \u4e0e\u5176\u4f59\u914d\u65b9\u4e0d\u53d8\uff0c\u6d4b\u8bd5\u662f\u5426\u80fd\u7528\u66f4\u4fbf\u5b9c\u7684 trunk \u76f4\u63a5\u62b9\u6389\u5f53\u524d\u4e3b\u8981\u7531 encoder cost \u5e26\u6765\u7684 objective \u7f3a\u53e3\u3002\u57fa\u4e8e\u672c\u5730 exact cost \u590d\u6838\uff0c`TRUNK_RANK=16 -> 8` \u4f1a\u628a combined_accesses \u4ece 835584 \u964d\u5230 778240\uff0c\u5bf9\u5f53\u524d 1024x4096 proxy \u7684 actual total_cost_ratio \u4ece\u7ea6 0.199219x \u964d\u5230\u7ea6 0.185547x\uff1b\u8fd9\u610f\u5473\u7740\u53ea\u8981 exceed \u7684\u56de\u5f39\u4e0d\u8d85\u8fc7\u7ea6 0.0137\uff0c\u672c\u8f6e\u5c31\u4f1a\u4f18\u4e8e r207\uff0c\u800c\u53ea\u8981 exceed \u4e0d\u9ad8\u4e8e\u7ea6 0.2006\uff0c\u5c31\u6709\u673a\u4f1a\u76f4\u63a5\u8d8a\u8fc7 incumbent r199\u3002",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0208.json:20:    "summary": "\u5efa\u8bae\u4ee5 r207 \u4e3a reference\uff0c\u53ea\u6539 `TRUNK_RANK=8`\u3002\u8fd9\u8f6e\u867d\u7136\u7559\u5728\u540c\u4e00 family\uff0c\u4f46\u4e0d\u662f\u4f4e\u4fe1\u606f\u7ec6\u626b\uff0c\u800c\u662f\u4e00\u4e2a\u76ee\u6807\u975e\u5e38\u660e\u786e\u7684 cost-dominant \u538b\u7f29\u9a8c\u8bc1\uff1ar207 \u5df2\u8bc1\u660e `lowrank_expert_topk` \u5728 `K=64 A=2 L=160` \u6253\u5f00\u4e86\u65b0\u7684\u4f4e\u6210\u672c lane\uff0c\u73b0\u5728\u6700\u6709\u4ef7\u503c\u7684\u95ee\u9898\u5c31\u662f\u518d\u538b trunk \u662f\u5426\u8db3\u4ee5\u628a objective \u76f4\u63a5\u63a8\u8fc7 incumbent\u3002",
