research/history/round_summaries/round_0277.json:26:    "self_review": "\u8fd9\u8f6e\u7b26\u5408\u5f53\u524d\u8fd0\u884c\u4f18\u5148\u7ea7\u3002r274-r276 \u5df2\u7ecf\u5728 dual-shared scaffold \u4e0a\u8fde\u7eed\u7ed9\u51fa\u4e0d\u591f\u5f3a\u7684 objective \u4fe1\u53f7\uff0c\u5176\u4e2d r275 \u867d\u6709\u6b63\u5411 exceed \u6539\u5584\uff0c\u4f46\u4ecd\u672a\u63a5\u8fd1 incumbent\uff0c\u800c r276 \u7684 adaptive \u53d8\u4f53\u53c8\u56de\u9000\uff1b\u6309\u89c4\u5219\u6b64\u65f6\u5e94\u4f18\u5148\u6362\u7ed3\u6784\u69fd\u4f4d\uff0c\u800c\u4e0d\u662f\u7ee7\u7eed\u5728\u540c\u4e00 scaffold \u4e0a\u505a split/active-path \u90bb\u57df\u7ec6\u626b\u3002\u9009\u62e9 `shared_lowrank_product_key_expert_jumprelu` \u800c\u4e0d\u662f\u7ee7\u7eed\u5806 dual-shared \u53d8\u4f53\uff0c\u662f\u56e0\u4e3a\u5b83\u66f4\u76f4\u63a5\u5bf9\u5e94\u5f53\u524d\u9ad8\u4f18\u5148\u7ea7\u65b9\u5411\u201cshared bottleneck + expert-specific head\u201d\uff0c\u540c\u65f6\u4fdd\u7559\u5f53\u524d\u5df2\u9a8c\u8bc1\u6709\u6548\u7684 PK cleanup \u8bed\u4e49\uff0c\u5e76\u4e14\u672c\u5730 exact cost \u590d\u6838\u843d\u5728 `~0.08x`\uff0c\u660e\u663e\u4f18\u4e8e `shared_lowrank_*` \u65e7\u5bb6\u65cf\u5728\u5f53\u524d 1024-expert recipe \u4e0b\u7684 `~0.19x` \u9ad8\u6210\u672c\u8d1f\u4fe1\u53f7\u3002\u4ee3\u7801\u4fa7\u53ea\u65b0\u589e\u6700\u5c0f family\uff0c\u5e76\u5b8c\u6210 whitelist\u3001factory dispatch\u3001override allowlist\u3001compatibility registry \u4e0e exact-string smoke\uff1b\u6ca1\u6709\u65b0\u589e tunable env key\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64\u4e0d\u9700\u8981\u6539 `config_resolution`\u3001`runner` \u6216 `scripts/autoresearch_test.sh`\u3002\u4e3b\u8981\u98ce\u9669\u662f\u4f4e\u79e9 shared bottleneck \u53ef\u80fd\u8fc7\u5f31\uff0cshared coarse \u53ea\u662f\u5728 cost \u4e0a\u66f4\u5de6\u5374\u6362\u4e0d\u56de\u8db3\u591f\u7684 exceed \u6539\u5584\uff1b\u4f46\u8fd9\u6b63\u662f\u4e00\u4e2a\u9ad8\u4fe1\u606f\u91cf\u3001\u8fd1\u540c\u6210\u672c\u7684\u65b0\u7ed3\u6784 probe\u3002",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0277.json:42:      "\u8be5 family \u4e0e `shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu` \u7684\u7cbe\u786e\u5dee\u5f02\u662f\uff1aalways-on shared branch \u4ece full `d_in -> latents` sparse encoder \u6539\u4e3a low-rank bottleneck `h(x)=ReLU(Bx)` \u4e0a\u7684 factorized shared coarse head\uff1b\u4e0e `shared_product_key_factorized_expert_topk` \u7684\u7cbe\u786e\u5dee\u5f02\u662f\uff1a\u53ea\u6709 shared coarse \u4e0e PK routing \u8d70\u4f4e\u79e9 hidden\uff0crouted expert cleanup \u4ecd\u4fdd\u7559 full `d_in -> latents_per_expert` expert encoders\uff0c\u800c\u4e0d\u662f factorized expert heads\u3002",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0277.json:47:      "\u517c\u5bb9\u6027\u6ce8\u518c\u8868\u5df2\u8865\u5145\u8be5 family\uff0c\u5f53\u524d\u89e3\u6790\u7ed3\u679c\u4e3a `direct_compatible`\uff1b\u66f4\u65b0\u540e\u672c\u5730\u8ba1\u6570\u4e3a\u76f4\u63a5\u517c\u5bb9 15 \u4e2a\u3001\u6269\u5c55\u517c\u5bb9 25 \u4e2a\u3001\u4e0d\u517c\u5bb9 3 \u4e2a\u3002",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0277.json:81:    "self_review": "\u8fd9\u8f6e\u7b26\u5408\u5f53\u524d\u8fd0\u884c\u4f18\u5148\u7ea7\u3002r274-r276 \u5df2\u7ecf\u5728 dual-shared scaffold \u4e0a\u8fde\u7eed\u7ed9\u51fa\u4e0d\u591f\u5f3a\u7684 objective \u4fe1\u53f7\uff0c\u5176\u4e2d r275 \u867d\u6709\u6b63\u5411 exceed \u6539\u5584\uff0c\u4f46\u4ecd\u672a\u63a5\u8fd1 incumbent\uff0c\u800c r276 \u7684 adaptive \u53d8\u4f53\u53c8\u56de\u9000\uff1b\u6309\u89c4\u5219\u6b64\u65f6\u5e94\u4f18\u5148\u6362\u7ed3\u6784\u69fd\u4f4d\uff0c\u800c\u4e0d\u662f\u7ee7\u7eed\u5728\u540c\u4e00 scaffold \u4e0a\u505a split/active-path \u90bb\u57df\u7ec6\u626b\u3002\u9009\u62e9 `shared_lowrank_product_key_expert_jumprelu` \u800c\u4e0d\u662f\u7ee7\u7eed\u5806 dual-shared \u53d8\u4f53\uff0c\u662f\u56e0\u4e3a\u5b83\u66f4\u76f4\u63a5\u5bf9\u5e94\u5f53\u524d\u9ad8\u4f18\u5148\u7ea7\u65b9\u5411\u201cshared bottleneck + expert-specific head\u201d\uff0c\u540c\u65f6\u4fdd\u7559\u5f53\u524d\u5df2\u9a8c\u8bc1\u6709\u6548\u7684 PK cleanup \u8bed\u4e49\uff0c\u5e76\u4e14\u672c\u5730 exact cost \u590d\u6838\u843d\u5728 `~0.08x`\uff0c\u660e\u663e\u4f18\u4e8e `shared_lowrank_*` \u65e7\u5bb6\u65cf\u5728\u5f53\u524d 1024-expert recipe \u4e0b\u7684 `~0.19x` \u9ad8\u6210\u672c\u8d1f\u4fe1\u53f7\u3002\u4ee3\u7801\u4fa7\u53ea\u65b0\u589e\u6700\u5c0f family\uff0c\u5e76\u5b8c\u6210 whitelist\u3001factory dispatch\u3001override allowlist\u3001compatibility registry \u4e0e exact-string smoke\uff1b\u6ca1\u6709\u65b0\u589e tunable env key\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64\u4e0d\u9700\u8981\u6539 `config_resolution`\u3001`runner` \u6216 `scripts/autoresearch_test.sh`\u3002\u4e3b\u8981\u98ce\u9669\u662f\u4f4e\u79e9 shared bottleneck \u53ef\u80fd\u8fc7\u5f31\uff0cshared coarse \u53ea\u662f\u5728 cost \u4e0a\u66f4\u5de6\u5374\u6362\u4e0d\u56de\u8db3\u591f\u7684 exceed \u6539\u5584\uff1b\u4f46\u8fd9\u6b63\u662f\u4e00\u4e2a\u9ad8\u4fe1\u606f\u91cf\u3001\u8fd1\u540c\u6210\u672c\u7684\u65b0\u7ed3\u6784 probe\u3002",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0099.json:19:    "hypothesis": "最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = Σ_{r=1..R} β_r(x) u_r + Σ_{i∈S_{e(x-t(x))}(x-t(x))} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i} + Σ_{j∈S_2(r_1)} γ_j(x) c_j，其中 t(x)=Σ_r β_r(x)u_r 是共享 low-rank trunk，{B_e} 是静态 expert 子库，r_1 = x - t(x) - Σ_{i∈S_{e(x-t(x))}(x-t(x))} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i}，C={c_j} 是静态 residual 补偿库。在线侧仍可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“trunk 查表 + 单个静态 expert 子库查表 + residual 补偿查表 + 有限加权和”推理链路，因此 `lowrank_expert_residual` 属于扩展兼容；`expert_topk` 属于直接兼容；`batch_topk` / `adaptive_budget_topk` 属于不兼容，不能驱动 frontier。唯一主假设是：r98 已经证明在 `K=96, TRUNK_RANK=40, NUM_EXPERTS=32` 的已压缩 recipe 上，residual cleanup 仍然非常有价值，FVU 从 matched `lowrank_expert_topk` 的 0.1305 明显压到 0.1030；因此当前最有信息量的问题不再是“要不要 residual”，而是该三段式结构在中等 deployment budget 下的最优 K 是否高于 96。相对 r98 仅将 `K: 96 -> 112`，如果这条 family 的主要收益不是偶然来自低 K 正则化，而是真的还受 lookup budget 限制，那么 FVU 应进一步低于 0.1030，并在约 total_cost=0.68x（selection≈0.53x，deployment≈0.15x）的可行带内形成更强的中低成本质量锚点。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0099.json:20:    "summary": "r98 已经把 matched `lowrank_expert_residual` 在压缩 recipe 上打成强正信号，因此本轮不再回到 `lowrank_expert_topk` 做局部边界补点，也不切去别的 family。以 r98 为 reference，只改 `K=112`，直接回答 residual cleanup 这条三段式主线在当前 target 上是否还受 deployment budget 限制，以及 `K=96` 是否已经低于它的最佳工作点。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0099.json:35:      "r98 (`lowrank_expert_residual K=96 TRUNK_RANK=40 NUM_EXPERTS=32`) 把 matched `lowrank_expert_topk` 的 0.1305 明显压到 0.1030，说明 residual cleanup 在当前 target 上不是边缘组件，而是强结构增益。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0099.json:63:    "description": "r98 已经把 matched `lowrank_expert_residual` 在压缩 recipe 上打成强正信号，因此本轮不再回到 `lowrank_expert_topk` 做局部边界补点，也不切去别的 family。以 r98 为 reference，只改 `K=112`，直接回答 residual cleanup 这条三段式主线在当前 target 上是否还受 deployment budget 限制，以及 `K=96` 是否已经低于它的最佳工作点。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0192.json:19:    "hypothesis": "候选 family 设为 `shared_two_stage_residual_expert`。最终重构公式为 `x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_sh(x)} α_i^sh(x) u_i + Σ_{e∈E(r)} Σ_{j∈S_e(r)} γ_{e,j}(r) c_{e,j}`，其中 `r = x - Σ_{i∈S_sh(x)} α_i^sh(x) u_i`，`{u_i}` 是 shared coarse 静态向量库，`{c_{e,j}}` 是 expert residual 静态子库。在线侧可直接导出为 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“shared coarse 查表+加权求和，再对 residual 做 expert 子库选择、查表与选择性补偿”流水线，静态库不随样本动态生成，因此兼容性判断为 `扩展兼容`。唯一主假设：相对 r190 仅切换到 `ARCHITECTURE=shared_two_stage_residual_expert`，在保持 `K=96`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1` 的 very-short-path low-cost recipe 下，显式把 cheap shared/coarse branch 与 expert residual cleanup 分工开来，会比当前 r190 的 `lowrank_expert_topk` 更有效地稳住 small-K 质量，并在约 `0.20x total_cost` 内把 FVU 明显压低。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0192.json:36:      "这轮不是继续沿 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 或 `lowrank_expert_topk` 做 K/LATENTS 插值，而是用当前最新可用 reference r190 做一次 matched-cost architecture swap，直接回答 small-K 下“cheap shared main branch + expert cleanup”是否比单 trunk+expert 更稳。"
research/history/round_summaries/round_0192.json:85:    "ARCHITECTURE": "lowrank_expert_topk",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0172.json:7:  "family_name": "shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0172.json:19:    "hypothesis": "候选 family 设为 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk`。最终重构公式可写为 `x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_sh(h(x))} α_i^sh(x) u_i + Σ_{e∈E(h(x))} Σ_{j∈S_e(x)} α_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j}`：其中 `{u_i}` 是由共享低秩 basis 导出的静态 shared 向量库，`{b_{e,j}}` 是 routed expert 的静态子库原子；在线侧先通过轻量 shared bottleneck / router 得到 shared 分支系数与少量激活 expert，再在对应静态库上做有限加权和。因此它仍可导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“shared 查表/加权和 + routed expert 子库查表 + 选择性补偿”流水线，兼容性判断为 `扩展兼容`；`batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk` 这类 batch/sample-coupled family 仍属不兼容，不能驱动当前 frontier。当前 round 172 的主问题不是继续在 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 或 `lowrank_expert_topk` 上补 `K/LATENTS_PER_EXPERT` 插值，而是寻找一个新的 `<0.25x` 结构槽位来挑战现有 low-cost anchor。相对 r171 只把 `ARCHITECTURE` 从 `lowrank_expert_topk` 切到 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk`，保持 `K=96`、`TRUNK_RANK=16`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=160`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`、`NUM_EXPERTS=64`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`adam`、`LR=8e-4` 不变，直接回答“在相同轻 trunk + 轻 routed recipe 下，加回一个更便宜的 shared bottleneck 分支，是否比纯 `lowrank_expert_topk` 更值得”。，基于当前成本口径复核，该配置仍位于预期成本带内并满足预算约束。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0172.json:20:    "summary": "以 r171 为 reference，仅切到 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk`，在保持 `K=96, TRUNK_RANK=16, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=160, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2` 不变的前提下，执行一个新的 matched-cost low-cost architecture probe，测试 `shared bottleneck + expert-specific head` 是否能在约 `0.22x` 成本下优于当前同带 anchors。",
