research/history/round_summaries/round_0070.json:162:    "ARCHITECTURE": "lowrank_expert_topk",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0078.json:19:    "hypothesis": "最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = Σ_e Σ_{i∈S_e(x)} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i}，其中 e(x) 是轻量 router 选出的单个 expert，{B_e} 是静态 expert 子库。导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的在线链路仍是“router 选单个静态子库 + 子库内 local top-k + 查表加权求和”，静态库不随样本动态生成，因此 `expert_topk` 属于直接兼容。兼容性先筛清楚：`expert_topk` 直接兼容；`factorized_expert_topk`、`lowrank_expert_topk`、`lowrank_expert_residual`、`two_stage_residual_expert` 属扩展兼容；`batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk` 等 batch/sample-coupled family 属不兼容，不能驱动 frontier。r77 已经给出清晰负信号：`factorized_expert_topk` 在与 r74 近同成本的 matched probe 下 FVU=0.2482，说明当前 `expert-internal low-rank / shared-basis` 原型不值得继续作为低成本主线。相对 r74 仅把 `K` 从 160 提到 192，在保持 `ARCHITECTURE=expert_topk`、`NUM_EXPERTS=128`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`OPTIMIZER=adam`、`LR=8e-4` 和其余训练配方不变时，直接回答 routed-only MoE-like 低成本前沿的下一关键问题：如果 r73→r74 的连续改善说明当前低成本带的主瓶颈仍有一部分来自每 token 的局部 lookup budget 不足，而不只是总容量，那么在保持同一容量与短 active path 的前提下，适度增加 `K` 应能在仍低于 0.5x total_cost 的范围内继续压低 FVU，并判断 routed-only 低成本线此刻更缺容量还是更缺 lookup budget。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0064.json:41:      "如果它明显弱于 r61，则可较清晰判定当前 target 上 low-rank trunk 是必要组成；后续应把预算回投到 `lowrank_expert_topk` 或 `lowrank_expert_residual`，而不是继续展开 trunk-free staged family。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0074.json:19:    "hypothesis": "最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = Σ_e Σ_{i∈S_e(x)} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i}，其中 e(x) 由轻量 router 选出的单个 expert，{B_e} 是静态 expert 子库。导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的在线链路仍是“router 选单个静态子库 + 子库内 local top-k + 查表加权求和”，静态库不随样本动态生成，因此 `expert_topk` 属于直接兼容。兼容性先筛清楚：`expert_topk` 直接兼容；`lowrank_expert_topk`、`lowrank_expert_residual`、`two_stage_residual_expert`、`factorized_expert_topk` 属扩展兼容；`batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk` 等 batch/sample-coupled family 属不兼容，不能继续驱动 frontier。相对 r73 仅把 `NUM_EXPERTS` 从 64 提到 128，在保持 `ARCHITECTURE=expert_topk`、`K=160`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`OPTIMIZER=adam`、`LR=8e-4` 和其余训练配方不变时，继续回答当前低成本带最关键的问题：如果 r73 的改善来自 true sparse-capacity MoE-like 扩容仍未吃满，而不是偶然训练波动，那么进一步放大总静态 expert 容量、同时保持 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1` 和相同查表路径长度，应能在近同一 total_cost 下继续压低 FVU，并把这条直接兼容的 routed-only 前沿继续向下推进。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0240.json:7:  "family_name": "hashed_expert_jumprelu",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0240.json:20:    "hypothesis": "\u6700\u7ec8\u91cd\u6784\u516c\u5f0f\u8bbe\u4e3a x_hat = \u03a3_{e\u2208E_hash(x)} \u03a3_{i\u2208\u015c_e(x)} \u03b1_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i}\uff0c\u5176\u4e2d {b_{e,i}} \u662f\u5404 expert \u7684\u9759\u6001\u5b50\u5e93\u539f\u5b50\uff0cE_hash(x) \u7531\u56fa\u5b9a sign-hash \u8def\u7531\u4ece\u8f93\u5165 x \u76f4\u63a5\u9009\u51fa\u5c11\u91cf active experts\uff0cexpert \u5185\u7cfb\u6570\u91c7\u7528 JumpReLU \u5f62\u5f0f \u03b1_{e,i}(x)=ReLU(z_{e,i})\u00b7\u03c3((ReLU(z_{e,i})-\u03c4_{e,i})/bandwidth)\u00b7p_e(x)\u3002\u5bfc\u51fa\u5230 LUTurbo/Lottable \u7684\u94fe\u8def\u4ecd\u662f\u201c\u56fa\u5b9a\u54c8\u5e0c\u8def\u7531\u9009\u62e9\u5c11\u91cf\u9759\u6001 expert \u5b50\u5e93 -> expert \u5185 JumpReLU sparse support -> \u9759\u6001\u5e93\u67e5\u8868\u52a0\u6743\u548c -> \u9009\u62e9\u6027\u8865\u507f\u201d\uff0c\u9759\u6001\u5e93\u4e0d\u968f\u6837\u672c\u52a8\u6001\u751f\u6210\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64\u65b0 family `hashed_expert_jumprelu` \u5224\u65ad\u4e3a\u76f4\u63a5\u517c\u5bb9\uff1b`batch_topk`\u3001`adaptive_budget_topk` \u7b49 batch/sample-coupled family \u4ecd\u5c5e\u4e0d\u517c\u5bb9\uff0c\u4e0d\u80fd\u9a71\u52a8\u5f53\u524d objective leaderboard\u3002\u672c\u8f6e\u4e3b\u5047\u8bbe\u662f\uff1ar238 \u4e0e r239 \u5df2\u8bf4\u660e variable-active-path \u548c low-rank trunk \u90fd\u6ca1\u6709\u628a objective \u771f\u6b63\u62c9\u4e0b\u6765\uff0c\u800c\u5f53\u524d incumbent \u7684\u4e3b\u8981\u77ed\u677f\u4ecd\u662f exceed \u8fc7\u9ad8\u4f46\u53c8\u4e0d\u80fd\u518d\u5bb9\u5fcd\u66f4\u91cd\u7ed3\u6784\uff1b\u56e0\u6b64\u76f8\u5bf9 r235 \u4ec5\u628a `ARCHITECTURE` \u4ece `expert_jumprelu` \u5207\u5230\u65b0\u5b9e\u73b0\u7684 `hashed_expert_jumprelu`\uff0c\u4fdd\u6301 `K=32, EF=1, adam, LR=8e-4, NUM_EXPERTS=128, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=192` \u4e0e\u5176\u4f59 recipe \u4e0d\u53d8\uff0c\u76f4\u63a5\u6d4b\u8bd5\u201c\u53bb\u6389 learned router\u3001\u4fdd\u7559 full expert heads + JumpReLU local supports\u201d\u80fd\u5426\u5728 exact total_cost_ratio=0.13623046875 \u7684\u66f4\u4f4e\u6210\u672c\u4e0b\uff0c\u628a exceed_alpha_0.50 \u63a7\u5236\u5728\u7ea6 0.21826 \u4ee5\u4e0b\uff0c\u4ece\u800c\u5237\u65b0\u5f53\u524d objective incumbent\u3002",
