research/history/round_summaries/round_0107.json:41:      "如果 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=384` 明显退化到接近或差于 `lowrank_expert_topk`，则可初步判定当前 shared+routed 收益仍依赖较宽 expert；后续应减少这条 family 的预算，把低成本探索切回 `lowrank_expert_topk` 的 `TRUNK_RANK` / `K` knee。",
