research/history/round_summaries/round_0271.json:25:    "self_review": "\u8fd9\u8f6e\u9075\u5b88\u5355\u53d8\u91cf\u539f\u5219\uff0c\u76f8\u5bf9 r266 \u53ea\u6539 `K`\u3002\u867d\u7136\u6700\u8fd1\u4e24\u8f6e\u6ca1\u6709\u628a objective \u518d\u5f80\u4e0b\u63a8\uff0c\u4f46\u5176\u4e2d\u4e00\u8f6e\u5df2\u7ecf\u6309\u89c4\u5219\u5207\u5230\u4e86\u65b0\u7ed3\u6784\u69fd\u4f4d `shared_product_key_factorized_expert_topk`\uff0c\u4e14\u7ed9\u51fa\u4e86\u6781\u5f3a\u8d1f\u4fe1\u53f7\uff1b\u5728\u8fd9\u79cd\u60c5\u51b5\u4e0b\uff0c\u76f4\u63a5\u7ee7\u7eed\u5207\u5230\u53e6\u4e00\u4e2a\u5df2\u591a\u6b21\u8d1f\u9762\u7684 family\uff0c\u4fe1\u606f\u589e\u91cf\u5e76\u4e0d\u6bd4\u628a\u5f53\u524d\u552f\u4e00 recent \u6b63\u4fe1\u53f7\u505a\u4e00\u6b21\u771f\u6b63\u7684\u5bb9\u91cf knee probe \u66f4\u9ad8\u3002\u9009\u62e9 `K=48` \u800c\u4e0d\u662f `K=40/64` \u7684\u539f\u56e0\u662f\uff1a`K=40` \u53ea\u9700\u8981\u7ea6 0.0098 \u7684 exceed \u6539\u5584\uff0c\u8fc7\u4e8e\u63a5\u8fd1\u5c0f\u4fee\u5c0f\u8865\uff1b`K=64` \u5219\u9700\u8981\u7ea6 0.039 \u7684 exceed \u6539\u5584\uff0c\u95e8\u69db\u504f\u786c\u3002`K=48` \u5904\u5728\u66f4\u5408\u7406\u7684\u4e2d\u95f4\u6863\uff0c\u65e2\u662f\u660e\u786e\u7684\u5bb9\u91cf\u6d4b\u8bd5\uff0c\u53c8\u4ecd\u4fdd\u7559\u73b0\u5b9e\u8d62\u9762\u3002\u4e3b\u8981\u98ce\u9669\u662f exceed \u4e0b\u964d\u5e45\u5ea6\u4e0d\u8db3\u4ee5\u8986\u76d6\u989d\u5916 deployment \u6210\u672c\uff0c\u5bfc\u81f4 objective \u4ecd\u4e0d\u5982 r266\uff1b\u4f46\u5982\u679c\u5982\u6b64\uff0c\u4e5f\u80fd\u66f4\u6e05\u6670\u5730\u8bf4\u660e\u5f53\u524d shared+PK \u7ebf\u5728 `K=32` \u9644\u8fd1\u5df2\u7ecf\u63a5\u8fd1\u5c40\u90e8 knee\uff0c\u540e\u7eed\u5e94\u56de\u5230\u65b0\u7684\u7ed3\u6784\u69fd\u4f4d\u800c\u4e0d\u662f\u7ee7\u7eed\u6cbf K \u8f74\u4e0a\u63a2\u3002",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0271.json:35:      "r270 `shared_product_key_factorized_expert_topk` \u5728\u5f53\u524d many-tiny 1024-bank/56-width recipe \u4e0b\u7ed9\u51fa\u6781\u5f3a\u8d1f\u4fe1\u53f7\uff1aobjective=0.500349\uff0ccost=0.115723\uff0cexceed=0.384626\uff0c\u4e14\u8bad\u7ec3\u66f2\u7ebf `curve_still_improving=false`\uff1b\u8fd9\u57fa\u672c\u5426\u5b9a\u4e86\u5f53\u524d hookpoint \u4e0a\u7684 tiny factorized experts \u65b9\u5411\u3002",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0271.json:73:    "self_review": "\u8fd9\u8f6e\u9075\u5b88\u5355\u53d8\u91cf\u539f\u5219\uff0c\u76f8\u5bf9 r266 \u53ea\u6539 `K`\u3002\u867d\u7136\u6700\u8fd1\u4e24\u8f6e\u6ca1\u6709\u628a objective \u518d\u5f80\u4e0b\u63a8\uff0c\u4f46\u5176\u4e2d\u4e00\u8f6e\u5df2\u7ecf\u6309\u89c4\u5219\u5207\u5230\u4e86\u65b0\u7ed3\u6784\u69fd\u4f4d `shared_product_key_factorized_expert_topk`\uff0c\u4e14\u7ed9\u51fa\u4e86\u6781\u5f3a\u8d1f\u4fe1\u53f7\uff1b\u5728\u8fd9\u79cd\u60c5\u51b5\u4e0b\uff0c\u76f4\u63a5\u7ee7\u7eed\u5207\u5230\u53e6\u4e00\u4e2a\u5df2\u591a\u6b21\u8d1f\u9762\u7684 family\uff0c\u4fe1\u606f\u589e\u91cf\u5e76\u4e0d\u6bd4\u628a\u5f53\u524d\u552f\u4e00 recent \u6b63\u4fe1\u53f7\u505a\u4e00\u6b21\u771f\u6b63\u7684\u5bb9\u91cf knee probe \u66f4\u9ad8\u3002\u9009\u62e9 `K=48` \u800c\u4e0d\u662f `K=40/64` \u7684\u539f\u56e0\u662f\uff1a`K=40` \u53ea\u9700\u8981\u7ea6 0.0098 \u7684 exceed \u6539\u5584\uff0c\u8fc7\u4e8e\u63a5\u8fd1\u5c0f\u4fee\u5c0f\u8865\uff1b`K=64` \u5219\u9700\u8981\u7ea6 0.039 \u7684 exceed \u6539\u5584\uff0c\u95e8\u69db\u504f\u786c\u3002`K=48` \u5904\u5728\u66f4\u5408\u7406\u7684\u4e2d\u95f4\u6863\uff0c\u65e2\u662f\u660e\u786e\u7684\u5bb9\u91cf\u6d4b\u8bd5\uff0c\u53c8\u4ecd\u4fdd\u7559\u73b0\u5b9e\u8d62\u9762\u3002\u4e3b\u8981\u98ce\u9669\u662f exceed \u4e0b\u964d\u5e45\u5ea6\u4e0d\u8db3\u4ee5\u8986\u76d6\u989d\u5916 deployment \u6210\u672c\uff0c\u5bfc\u81f4 objective \u4ecd\u4e0d\u5982 r266\uff1b\u4f46\u5982\u679c\u5982\u6b64\uff0c\u4e5f\u80fd\u66f4\u6e05\u6670\u5730\u8bf4\u660e\u5f53\u524d shared+PK \u7ebf\u5728 `K=32` \u9644\u8fd1\u5df2\u7ecf\u63a5\u8fd1\u5c40\u90e8 knee\uff0c\u540e\u7eed\u5e94\u56de\u5230\u65b0\u7684\u7ed3\u6784\u69fd\u4f4d\u800c\u4e0d\u662f\u7ee7\u7eed\u6cbf K \u8f74\u4e0a\u63a2\u3002",
research/history/logs/agent_action_0260.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"候选 family 设为 `product_key_factorized_expert_topk`。最终重构公式为 `x_hat = Σ_{e∈E_pk(h(x))} Σ_{j∈S_e(h(x))} γ_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j}`，其中 `h(x)` 是共享 low-rank bottleneck，`{b_{e,j}}` 是各 routed factorized expert 的静态子库原子，`E_pk(h(x))` 由 left/right product-key router 在 expert 对上给出组合式寻址，随后每个激活 expert 只在自己的静态子库内做 local top-k 并输出有限加权和。导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的在线链路仍是“共享 low-rank bottleneck -> product-key expert 选择 -> routed tiny factorized expert 子库查表/加权和 -> 选择性补偿”，静态库不随样本动态生成，因此兼容性判断为直接兼容。它与 `factorized_expert_topk` 的精确差异不是重命名，而是把 flat `hidden_dim -> num_experts` router 改成了 compositional product-key routing；它与刚失败的 `shared_product_key_factorized_expert_topk` 的精确差异则是去掉了 always-on shared 分支，专门隔离“tiny factorized experts 失败到底是 flat router 的锅，还是 shared+tiny 组合本身就不行”。相对 r235 只把 `ARCHITECTURE` 从 `expert_jumprelu` 切到新 family，保持 `K=32`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`OPTIMIZER=adam`、`LR=8e-4`、`NUM_EXPERTS=128`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=192`、`FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256` 与其余主 recipe 不变，直接回答当前剩余最高信息量的问题：在同样的 matched lane 下，单靠 product-key compositional routing 是否足以把低成本 tiny factorized expert 方向拉回到值得继续的 objective 区间。按本地 exact 成本复核，该 matched probe 的 selection_accesses=366336、deployment_accesses=163840、combined_accesses=530176、exact total_cost_ratio=0.12640380859375，仍明显低于预算；若要打赢本地 r235 exact objective=0.358553，则需要把 `exceed_alpha_0.50` 压到 `0.23214919140625` 以下。这个门槛明显宽于 round259 那条 shared+PK+tiny family 的 `0.2204` 门槛，因此它是当前更干净、也更有现实胜面的 router-isolation probe。","summary":"已实际新增并注册 `product_key_factorized_expert_topk`。建议以 r235 为 reference，只改 `ARCHITECTURE=product_key_factorized_expert_topk`，做一轮新的 matched architecture probe，直接判断“PK routing 能不能救活 tiny factorized experts”这个结构槽位本身值不值得继续。","change_type":"edit_sae_code","expected_win":"explore_unknown","family_name":"product_key_factorized_expert_topk","family_stage":"prototype","self_review":"这轮继续满足 Round 260 的核心约束：只做 1 个 architecture probe，并且相对 reference 只改 `ARCHITECTURE`。之所以不继续围绕 round259 那条 `shared_product_key_factorized_expert_topk` 细扫，是因为它已经给出灾难性负信号：exact `0.1381x` 的低成本下 exceed 仍飙到 `0.4168`，说明 shared+tiny factorized 这条组合本身极不稳。之所以不回到 `factorized_expert_topk` 原 family，则是因为它在同一 matched lane 的旧结果同样很差，但旧结果不能回答问题到底在 tiny factorized heads，还是在 flat router。新 family 的信息增量正好在这里：保持 tiny factorized experts 不变，只把路由器换成 product-key，并且去掉刚刚证明有害的 shared 分支。主要风险也很清楚：如果 tiny factorized expert heads 本身就是主瓶颈，那么即使 product-key router 把 expert addressing 做得更好，也可能仍然无法把 exceed 拉回可竞争区间；但这正是本轮要一次性关掉或保留的结构问题。","needs_sanity":true,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"product_key_factorized_expert_topk"}],"touched_files":["sparsify/config.py","sparsify/sparse_coder.py","research/AutoResearch/override_registry.py"],"notes_to_memory":["round259 已给出 `shared_product_key_factorized_expert_topk` 的强负信号：objective=0.554925、cost=0.138123x、exceed=0.416802，说明 `shared bottleneck + PK routing + tiny factorized experts` 这条组合在当前 matched lane 下完全不值得继续主导预算。","已实际新增并注册 `product_key_factorized_expert_topk`，真实落盘文件只有 `sparsify/config.py`、`sparsify/sparse_coder.py`、`research/AutoResearch/override_registry.py`；没有新增 tunable env key，也没有改 `scripts/autoresearch_test.sh`。","新 family 的结构语义是 `low-rank bottleneck + product-key routed factorized experts`：这不是 `factorized_expert_topk` 的别名，因为 routed expert 选择从 flat hidden router 改成了 compositional product-key expert addressing；也不是 `shared_product_key_factorized_expert_topk` 的别名，因为它移除了 always-on shared factorized branch。","本地 exact architecture smoke 已通过：`SparseCoderConfig(architecture='product_key_factorized_expert_topk', k=32, expansion_factor=1, num_experts=128, active_experts=2, latents_per_expert=192, factorized_hidden_dim=256)` 在 CPU 上可成功 instantiate、forward、backward。","本地 override allowlist 自检已通过：`validate_env_overrides([{key:'ARCHITECTURE', value:'product_key_factorized_expert_topk'}], fallback_architecture='expert_jumprelu')` 返回空列表；连同 `NUM_EXPERTS/ACTIVE_EXPERTS/LATENTS_PER_EXPERT/FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM` 的组合校验也返回空列表。","本地 exact 成本复核：`product_key_factorized_expert_topk K=32 EF=1 NUM_EXPERTS=128 ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2 LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=192 FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256` 的 selection_accesses=366336、deployment_accesses=163840、combined_accesses=530176、exact total_cost_ratio=0.12640380859375；打赢本地 r235 exact objective=0.358553 所需阈值为 `exceed_alpha_0.50 < 0.23214919140625`。","当前工作区真实兼容 frontier 仍以 `research/history/frontier.json` 为准：best compatible point 依然是 r251 `product_key_expert_jumprelu`，而不是 prompt 里的旧 `expert_jumprelu` anchor；本轮只把 r235 当 matched architecture probe 的 patch anchor。"],"next_hypotheses":["如果 `product_key_factorized_expert_topk` 能把 exceed 压到 `0.23` 以下并在 matched lane 上接近或打赢 r235，则下一轮应继续留在该 family，只改 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM`，判断 tiny factorized expert 头宽度是不是这条低成本 PK 线的主控制旋钮。","如果它的 objective 仍明显输给 r235，尤其是 exceed 继续停在 `0.28+` 或更差区间，则可以更明确地关闭“PK router 能救活 tiny factorized experts”这个方向；后续结构预算不应再继续围绕 factorized expert 家族细扫。","如果它比旧 `factorized_expert_topk` 有明显改善但仍不够 competitive，则可把结论记为：product-key router 对 tiny factorized expert lane 有帮助，但不足以单独解决 objective 缺口；之后若还追这一方向，更可能需要回到 full expert heads 或引入 genuinely different residual cleanup，而不是继续只换路由器。"],"reference_round":235}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0259.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"候选 family 设为 `shared_product_key_factorized_expert_topk`。最终重构公式为 `x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_sh(h(x))} α_i^sh(x) u_i + Σ_{e∈E_pk(h(x))} Σ_{j∈S_e(h(x))} γ_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j}`，其中 `h(x)` 是共享 low-rank bottleneck，`{u_i}` 是 always-on shared 静态向量库，`{b_{e,j}}` 是各 routed factorized expert 的静态子库原子，`E_pk(h(x))` 由 left/right product-key router 在 expert 对上给出组合式寻址。导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的在线链路仍是“共享 low-rank bottleneck -> shared 子库查表/加权和 + product-key expert 选择 -> routed tiny factorized expert 子库查表/加权和 -> 选择性补偿”，静态库不随样本动态生成，因此兼容性判断为直接兼容。它与现有 `shared_routed_factorized_expert_topk` 的精确差异不是重命名，而是把 flat `hidden_dim -> num_experts` router 换成了 compositional product-key routing；与刚失败的 `shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu` 的精确差异则是把高成本的 full-dim residual expert 头换成 tiny factorized expert heads，明确测试“PK 路由能否救活 shared bottleneck + tiny experts 这条低成本槽位”。相对 r235 只把 `ARCHITECTURE` 从 `expert_jumprelu` 切到新 family，保持 `K=32`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`OPTIMIZER=adam`、`LR=8e-4`、`NUM_EXPERTS=128`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=192`、`FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256` 与其余主 recipe 不变，直接回答当前高优先级但尚未被当前实现覆盖的问题：当 shared bottleneck 与 tiny routed experts 已知本身都偏弱时，product-key compositional routing 是否足以把这条 low-cost lane 拉回到值得继续的 objective 区间。按本地 exact 成本复核，该 matched probe 的 selection_accesses=415488、deployment_accesses=163840、combined_accesses=579328、exact total_cost_ratio=0.1381072998046875，仍明显低于预算；若要打赢本地 r235 exact objective=0.358553，则需要把 `exceed_alpha_0.50` 压到 `0.22044570019531247` 以下。这个门槛明显低于 round258 那条 `shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu` 的 `0.1733` 门槛，因此它是当前更合理的“shared/product-key/tiny-expert” matched slot closure probe。","summary":"已实际新增并注册 `shared_product_key_factorized_expert_topk`。建议以 r235 为 reference，只改 `ARCHITECTURE=shared_product_key_factorized_expert_topk`，做一轮新的 matched architecture probe，直接判断“shared bottleneck + PK routing + tiny factorized experts”这个低成本结构槽位本身值不值得继续。","change_type":"edit_sae_code","expected_win":"explore_unknown","family_name":"shared_product_key_factorized_expert_topk","family_stage":"prototype","self_review":"这轮继续遵守 Round 259 的核心约束：只做 1 个 architecture probe，并且相对 reference 只改 `ARCHITECTURE`。之所以不继续重复 `shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu` 或其他已测 shared/coarse family，是因为 round258 已给出清晰负信号：shared coarse + PK residual full heads 在 exact `0.1853x` 下仍只把 exceed 压到 `0.1829`，objective 明显不够；继续沿那条线补参数会变成 prompt 明确下调优先级的低信息细扫。之所以不回到 `shared_routed_factorized_expert_topk` 原 family，是因为它在同 lane 的旧结果很差，但旧结论并不能回答“问题到底在 shared+tiny experts，还是在 flat router”。新 family 的信息增量正好在这里：保持 shared + tiny factorized experts 不变，只把路由机制换成 product-key compositional addressing。主要风险也很清楚：如果 factorized expert heads 本身就是主要瓶颈，那么即使 PK router 降低选择难度，也可能仍然挡不住 exceed；但这正是本轮要干净回答的结构问题。","needs_sanity":true,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"shared_product_key_factorized_expert_topk"}],"touched_files":["sparsify/config.py","sparsify/sparse_coder.py","research/AutoResearch/override_registry.py"],"notes_to_memory":["round258 已给出 `shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu` 的清晰负信号：objective=0.368166、cost=0.185303x、exceed=0.182863；说明“shared coarse + PK residual full heads”在当前 matched lane 下不值得继续主导预算。","已实际新增并注册 `shared_product_key_factorized_expert_topk`，真实落盘文件只有 `sparsify/config.py`、`sparsify/sparse_coder.py`、`research/AutoResearch/override_registry.py`；没有新增 tunable env key，也没有改 `scripts/autoresearch_test.sh`。","新 family 的结构语义是 `shared factorized branch + product-key routed factorized experts`：这不是 `shared_routed_factorized_expert_topk` 的别名，因为 routed expert 选择从 flat hidden router 改成了 compositional product-key expert addressing；也不是 `shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu` 的别名，因为 routed expert 头从 full-dim JumpReLU cleanup 换成了 tiny factorized heads。","本地 exact architecture smoke 已通过：`SparseCoderConfig(architecture='shared_product_key_factorized_expert_topk', k=32, expansion_factor=1, num_experts=128, active_experts=2, latents_per_expert=192, factorized_hidden_dim=256)` 在 CPU 上可成功 instantiate、forward、backward。","本地 override allowlist 自检已通过：`validate_env_overrides([{key:'ARCHITECTURE', value:'shared_product_key_factorized_expert_topk'}], fallback_architecture='expert_jumprelu')` 返回空列表；连同 `NUM_EXPERTS/ACTIVE_EXPERTS/LATENTS_PER_EXPERT/FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM` 的组合校验也返回空列表。","本地 exact 成本复核：`shared_product_key_factorized_expert_topk K=32 EF=1 NUM_EXPERTS=128 ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2 LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=192 FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256` 的 selection_accesses=415488、deployment_accesses=163840、combined_accesses=579328、exact total_cost_ratio=0.1381072998046875；打赢本地 r235 exact objective=0.358553 所需阈值为 `exceed_alpha_0.50 < 0.22044570019531247`。","当前工作区真实兼容 frontier 仍以 `research/history/frontier.json` 为准：best compatible point 依然是 r251 `product_key_expert_jumprelu`，而不是 prompt 里的旧 `expert_jumprelu` anchor；本轮只把 r235 当 matched architecture probe 的 patch anchor。"],"next_hypotheses":["如果 `shared_product_key_factorized_expert_topk` surprisingly 把 exceed 压到 `0.22` 以下并在 matched lane 上接近或打赢 r235，则下一轮应继续留在该 family，只改 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM`，判断 tiny expert 头宽度是不是这条低成本 PK+shared 线的主控制旋钮。","如果它的 objective 仍明显输给 r235，尤其是 exceed 继续停在 `0.25+` 或更差区间，则可以更明确地下调“shared bottleneck + tiny factorized experts”这一整类结构在当前 target 上的优先级；后续结构预算应回到别的 genuinely new slot，而不是继续围绕 factorized expert 家族细扫。","如果它比 `shared_routed_factorized_expert_topk` 有明显改善但仍不够 competitive，则可把结论记为：product-key router 对 shared+tiny-expert lane 有帮助，但不足以单独解决 objective 缺口；之后若还追这条方向，更可能需要额外的 residual cleanup 或 variable-active-path，而不是继续只换路由器。"],"reference_round":235}
research/history/round_summaries/round_0270.json:7:  "family_name": "shared_product_key_factorized_expert_topk",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0270.json:19:    "hypothesis": "\u6700\u7ec8\u91cd\u6784\u516c\u5f0f\u5199\u4e3a x_hat = \u03a3_{i\u2208S_sh(x)} \u03b1_i^sh(x) b_i^sh + \u03a3_{e\u2208E_pk(x)} \u03a3_{j\u2208S_e(x)} \u03b3_{e,j}(x) c_{e,j}\uff0c\u5176\u4e2d\u7b2c\u4e00\u9879\u662f always-on shared coarse \u9759\u6001\u5e93\u7684\u6709\u9650\u52a0\u6743\u548c\uff0c\u7b2c\u4e8c\u9879\u662f\u5728 product-key \u9009\u51fa\u7684\u5c11\u91cf\u9759\u6001 expert \u5b50\u5e93\u5185\uff0c\u7528 factorized local head \u4ea7\u751f\u7cfb\u6570\u540e\u7684\u7a00\u758f\u67e5\u8868\u52a0\u6743\u548c\uff1b\u4e0e `shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu` \u7684\u5dee\u5f02\u4e0d\u5728 shared/PK \u5206\u5de5\uff0c\u800c\u5728 expert \u5185\u90e8\u4ece full-dim local head \u6539\u6210 tiny factorized head\u3002\u5bfc\u51fa\u5230 LUTurbo/Lottable \u7684\u5728\u7ebf\u94fe\u8def\u4ecd\u662f\u201cshared \u67e5\u8868 -> PK \u8def\u7531\u5230\u9759\u6001 expert \u5b50\u5e93 -> expert \u5185\u5c40\u90e8 sparse support -> \u67e5\u8868\u52a0\u6743\u548c -> \u9009\u62e9\u6027\u8865\u507f\u201d\uff0c\u4e0d\u6d89\u53ca\u52a8\u6001\u5b57\u5178\u751f\u6210\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64 `shared_product_key_factorized_expert_topk` \u5224\u5b9a\u4e3a\u76f4\u63a5\u517c\u5bb9\uff1b\u4e0d\u517c\u5bb9 family `batch_topk`\u3001`adaptive_budget_topk`\u3001`lowrank_adaptive_budget_residual` \u7ee7\u7eed\u53ea\u4f5c\u5386\u53f2\u53c2\u8003\uff0c\u4e0d\u53c2\u4e0e\u5f53\u524d\u517c\u5bb9 leaderboard\u3002r268 \u4e0e r269 \u5df2\u628a `shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu` \u7684 split \u8f74\u57fa\u672c\u88c1\u6e05\uff1a\u5728\u5b8c\u5168\u540c exact cost 0.095703125 \u4e0b\uff0c`STAGE1_RATIO=0.25` \u4f18\u4e8e `0.5` \u4e0e `0.125`\uff0c\u8bf4\u660e\u5f53\u524d family \u7684\u9ad8\u4ef7\u503c\u5c40\u90e8\u5047\u8bbe\u5df2\u57fa\u672c\u6536\u655b\uff0c\u4e0d\u5e94\u7ee7\u7eed\u5728\u540c family \u4e0a\u7ec6\u626b\u3002\u4e0b\u4e00\u8f6e\u66f4\u6709\u4fe1\u606f\u91cf\u7684\u95ee\u9898\u5e94\u56de\u5230\u65b0\u7684\u7ed3\u678